lass=\"\" data-start=\"1384\" data-end=\"1387\" />\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1389\" data-end=\"1416\"><strong data-start=\"1389\" data-end=\"1414\">Storage and Handling:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1417\" data-end=\"1587\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1417\" data-end=\"1459\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1419\" data-end=\"1459\">Store lyophilized powder at <strong data-start=\"1447\" data-end=\"1456\">-20°C</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1460\" data-end=\"1520\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1462\" data-end=\"1520\">Once reconstituted, store at <strong data-start=\"1491\" data-end=\"1500\">2-8°C</strong> and use promptly.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1521\" data-end=\"1587\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1523\" data-end=\"1587\">Maintain aseptic techniques during handling to ensure sterility.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"1589\" data-end=\"1592\" />\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1594\" data-end=\"1623\"><strong data-start=\"1594\" data-end=\"1621\">Product Specifications:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1624\" data-end=\"1755\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1624\" data-end=\"1660\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1626\" data-end=\"1660\"><strong data-start=\"1626\" data-end=\"1637\">Purity:</strong> ≥99% (HPLC Verified)</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1661\" data-end=\"1705\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1663\" data-end=\"1705\"><strong data-start=\"1663\" data-end=\"1678\">Appearance:</strong> Lyophilized white powder</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1706\" data-end=\"1755\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1708\" data-end=\"1755\"><strong data-start=\"1708\" data-end=\"1723\">Solubility:</strong> Soluble in bacteriostatic water</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"1757\" data-end=\"1760\" />\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1762\" data-end=\"2344\"><strong data-start=\"1762\" data-end=\"1781\">Important Note:</strong><br data-start=\"1781\" data-end=\"1784\" />Semax is strictly <strong data-start=\"1802\" data-end=\"1827\">FOR RESEARCH USE ONLY</strong> and is intended exclusively for in vitro research and laboratory experimentation by qualified professionals. It is <strong data-start=\"1943\" data-end=\"1950\">not</strong> a drug, food, cosmetic, or dietary supplement and has not been evaluated by the FDA. This peptide is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. Introduction into humans or animals is strictly prohibited by law. Any misuse, misbranding, or mislabeling is a violation of federal regulations and may result in legal consequences under applicable federal, state, or local laws.</p>\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"2346\" data-end=\"2349\" />\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2351\" data-end=\"2412\"><strong data-start=\"2351\" data-end=\"2366\">References:</strong><br data-start=\"2366\" data-end=\"2369\" />Referenced scientific publications include:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"2414\" data-end=\"2657\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2414\" data-end=\"2527\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2416\" data-end=\"2527\">Ashmarin, I. P., et al. (2000). <em data-start=\"2448\" data-end=\"2489\">“Semax: A New Neuroprotective Peptide.”</em> Neuroscience &amp; Behavioral Physiology.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2528\" data-end=\"2657\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2530\" data-end=\"2657\">Myasoedov, N. F., et al. (2008). <em data-start=\"2563\" data-end=\"2630\">“The Role of Semax in Neuroprotection and Cognitive Enhancement.”</em> Journal of Neurochemistry.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>',75.00,39.00,NULL,10.00,'in_stock','active',2,NULL,0,0,0,'https://myoasislabs.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Semax-scaled.jpg','https://myoasislabs.com/product/semax-10mg/','2025-12-04 13:37:06','2025-12-04 13:37:06',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,69),(76,'SS-31 10mg','<p class=\"\" data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"79\"><strong data-start=\"20\" data-end=\"77\">SS-31 (Elamipretide / Mitochondria-Targeting Peptide)</strong></p>\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"81\" data-end=\"84\" />\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"86\" data-end=\"113\"><strong data-start=\"86\" data-end=\"111\">Chemical Information:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"114\" data-end=\"361\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"114\" data-end=\"153\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"116\" data-end=\"153\"><strong data-start=\"116\" data-end=\"138\">Molecular Formula:</strong> C₄₉H₈₇N₁₃O₁₀</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"154\" data-end=\"191\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"156\" data-end=\"191\"><strong data-start=\"156\" data-end=\"177\">Molecular Weight:</strong> 936.3 g/mol</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"192\" data-end=\"264\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"194\" data-end=\"264\"><strong data-start=\"194\" data-end=\"207\">Sequence:</strong> D-Arg-Dmt-Lys-Phe-NH₂ <em data-start=\"230\" data-end=\"262\">(Dmt = 2&#8242;,6&#8242;-dimethyltyrosine)</em></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"265\" data-end=\"361\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"267\" data-end=\"361\"><strong data-start=\"267\" data-end=\"291\">Molecular Structure:</strong> Refer to Certificate of Analysis for detailed structural information.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"363\" data-end=\"366\" />\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"368\" data-end=\"895\"><strong data-start=\"368\" data-end=\"384\">Description:</strong><br data-start=\"384\" data-end=\"387\" />SS-31, also known as Elamipretide, is a synthetic tetrapeptide designed to selectively target the inner mitochondrial membrane. Extensively researched for its ability to improve mitochondrial function and reduce oxidative stress, SS-31 plays a promising role in studies involving cellular energy production, mitochondrial dynamics, and degenerative disease models. Supplied in lyophilized powder form, SS-31 is formulated for research focused on bioenergetics, oxidative damage, and mitochondrial protection.</p>\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"897\" data-end=\"900\" />\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"902\" data-end=\"980\"><strong data-start=\"902\" data-end=\"928\">Research Applications:</strong><br data-start=\"928\" data-end=\"931\" />SS-31 is actively studied for its potential to:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"981\" data-end=\"1551\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"981\" data-end=\"1115\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"983\" data-end=\"1115\"><strong data-start=\"983\" data-end=\"1018\">Enhance Mitochondrial Function:</strong> Investigate improvements in mitochondrial ATP production and membrane potential stabilization.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1116\" data-end=\"1259\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1118\" data-end=\"1259\"><strong data-start=\"1118\" data-end=\"1146\">Reduce Oxidative Stress:</strong> Explore its antioxidant-like effects by neutralizing reactive oxygen species (ROS) at the mitochondrial level.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1260\" data-end=\"1400\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1262\" data-end=\"1400\"><strong data-start=\"1262\" data-end=\"1301\">Support Cellular Energy Metabolism:</strong> Study its influence on metabolic efficiency and recovery in models of mitochondrial dysfunction.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1401\" data-end=\"1551\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1403\" data-end=\"1551\"><strong data-start=\"1403\" data-end=\"1447\">Protect Against Degenerative Conditions:</strong> Evaluate its role in research involving cardiovascular, muscular, and neurodegenerative disease models.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"1553\" data-end=\"1556\" />\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1558\" data-end=\"1585\"><strong data-start=\"1558\" data-end=\"1583\">Storage and Handling:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1586\" data-end=\"1770\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1586\" data-end=\"1628\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1588\" data-end=\"1628\">Store lyophilized powder at <strong data-start=\"1616\" data-end=\"1625\">-20°C</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1629\" data-end=\"1691\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1631\" data-end=\"1691\">After reconstitution, store at <strong data-start=\"1662\" data-end=\"1671\">2-8°C</strong> and use promptly.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1692\" data-end=\"1770\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1694\" data-end=\"1770\">Handle under aseptic conditions to preserve sterility and product stability.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"1772\" data-end=\"1775\" />\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1777\" data-end=\"1806\"><strong data-start=\"1777\" data-end=\"1804\">Product Specifications:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1807\" data-end=\"1968\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1807\" data-end=\"1843\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1809\" data-end=\"1843\"><strong data-start=\"1809\" data-end=\"1820\">Purity:</strong> ≥99% (HPLC Verified)</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1844\" data-end=\"1901\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1846\" data-end=\"1901\"><strong data-start=\"1846\" data-end=\"1861\">Appearance:</strong> Lyophilized white to off-white powder</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1902\" data-end=\"1968\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1904\" data-end=\"1968\"><strong data-start=\"1904\" data-end=\"1919\">Solubility:</strong> Soluble in sterile water or bacteriostatic water</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"1970\" data-end=\"1973\" />\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1975\" data-end=\"2558\"><strong data-start=\"1975\" data-end=\"1994\">Important Note:</strong><br data-start=\"1994\" data-end=\"1997\" />SS-31 is strictly <strong data-start=\"2015\" data-end=\"2040\">FOR RESEARCH USE ONLY</strong> and is intended exclusively for in vitro research and laboratory experimentation by qualified professionals. It is <strong data-start=\"2156\" data-end=\"2163\">not</strong> a drug, food, cosmetic, or dietary supplement and has not been evaluated by the FDA. This compound is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. Introduction into humans or animals is strictly prohibited by law. Any misuse, misbranding, or mislabeling is a violation of federal regulations and may result in legal consequences under applicable federal, state, or local laws.</p>\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"2560\" data-end=\"2563\" />\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2565\" data-end=\"2626\"><strong data-start=\"2565\" data-end=\"2580\">References:</strong><br data-start=\"2580\" data-end=\"2583\" />Referenced scientific publications include:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"2628\" data-end=\"3028\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2628\" data-end=\"2739\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2630\" data-end=\"2739\">Szeto, H. H., et al. (2008). <em data-start=\"2659\" data-end=\"2725\">“Mitochondria-Targeted Peptides: A Novel Class of Therapeutics.”</em> Aging Cell.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2740\" data-end=\"2883\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2742\" data-end=\"2883\">Zhao, K., et al. (2005). <em data-start=\"2767\" data-end=\"2848\">“Cell-permeable Peptide Antioxidants Targeted to Inner Mitochondrial Membrane.”</em> Journal of Biological Chemistry.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2884\" data-end=\"3028\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2886\" data-end=\"3028\">Daubert, M. A., et al. (2017). <em data-start=\"2917\" data-end=\"2990\">“Elamipretide Improves Mitochondrial Function in Failing Human Hearts.”</em> JACC: Basic to Translational Science.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>',80.00,49.00,NULL,10.00,'in_stock','active',2,NULL,0,0,0,'https://myoasislabs.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/SS-31-scaled.jpg','https://myoasislabs.com/product/ss-31-10mg/','2025-12-04 13:37:06','2025-12-04 13:37:06',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,45),(77,'BAC Water 3ml','<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"440\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"29\">Bacteriostatic Water 0.9%</strong> is a sterile, non-pyrogenic solution containing 0.9% benzyl alcohol as a preservative. It is specifically prepared for laboratory research applications, intended primarily as a solvent or diluent for peptide reconstitution and other compatible substances in controlled experimental settings. The benzyl alcohol present helps inhibit bacterial growth, facilitating multiple withdrawals under aseptic conditions.</p>\n<p data-start=\"442\" data-end=\"472\"><strong data-start=\"442\" data-end=\"470\">Product Characteristics:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"473\" data-end=\"726\">\n<li data-start=\"473\" data-end=\"493\"><strong data-start=\"475\" data-end=\"486\">Volume:</strong> 30mL</li>\n<li data-start=\"494\" data-end=\"559\"><strong data-start=\"496\" data-end=\"512\">Composition:</strong> Sterile water containing 0.9% benzyl alcohol</li>\n<li data-start=\"560\" data-end=\"643\"><strong data-start=\"562\" data-end=\"574\">Purpose:</strong> Solvent/diluent for peptide reconstitution and laboratory research</li>\n<li data-start=\"644\" data-end=\"726\"><strong data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"665\">Multi-use vial:</strong> Designed for multiple withdrawals under aseptic conditions</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"747\"><strong data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"745\">Intended Use:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"748\" data-end=\"894\">\n<li data-start=\"748\" data-end=\"790\">For laboratory research purposes only.</li>\n<li data-start=\"791\" data-end=\"894\">Not intended for human or veterinary use, including medical, therapeutic, or diagnostic applications.</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"896\" data-end=\"921\"><strong data-start=\"896\" data-end=\"919\">Storage &amp; Handling:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"922\" data-end=\"1257\">\n<li data-start=\"922\" data-end=\"1006\">Store unopened vials at controlled room temperature: 20°C to 25°C (68°F to 77°F)</li>\n<li data-start=\"1007\" data-end=\"1085\">After first puncture, store under refrigeration: 2°C to 8°C (36°F to 46°F)</li>\n<li data-start=\"1086\" data-end=\"1103\">Do not freeze</li>\n<li data-start=\"1104\" data-end=\"1152\">Use aseptic techniques to maintain sterility</li>\n<li data-start=\"1153\" data-end=\"1257\">Discard any unused portion within 28 days of first puncture 