Glu-Gln-Glu-Val-Val-Glu-Ala-Glu-Asn-OH</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"306\" data-end=\"309\" />\n<p data-start=\"311\" data-end=\"856\"><strong data-start=\"311\" data-end=\"327\">Description:</strong><br data-start=\"327\" data-end=\"330\" />Thymosin Alpha-1 is a naturally derived peptide fragment originating from prothymosin alpha, recognized for its immunomodulatory effects. In research studies, Thymosin Alpha-1 has demonstrated potential to enhance T-cell function, regulate immune responses, and moderate inflammatory pathways. Its role is extensively studied in contexts of immune response regulation, inflammatory control, infection resistance, and immune-oncology. Provided in lyophilized powder form, Thymosin Alpha-1 is strictly intended for research use.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"858\" data-end=\"861\" />\n<p data-start=\"863\" data-end=\"952\"><strong data-start=\"863\" data-end=\"889\">Research Applications:</strong><br data-start=\"889\" data-end=\"892\" />Current research explores Thymosin Alpha-1’s potential to:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"953\" data-end=\"1461\">\n<li data-start=\"953\" data-end=\"1066\"><strong data-start=\"955\" data-end=\"983\">Enhance Immune Activity:</strong> Examining its capacity to stimulate T-cell function and modulate immune responses.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1067\" data-end=\"1175\"><strong data-start=\"1069\" data-end=\"1093\">Reduce Inflammation:</strong> Investigating its influence on inflammation regulation and immune system balance.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1176\" data-end=\"1303\"><strong data-start=\"1178\" data-end=\"1209\">Support Infection Research:</strong> Evaluating its potential effects in enhancing defenses against viral and bacterial pathogens.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1304\" data-end=\"1461\"><strong data-start=\"1306\" data-end=\"1336\">Advance Oncology Research:</strong> Assessing its possible contributions in cancer immunotherapy, particularly regarding immune surveillance and responsiveness.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1463\" data-end=\"1466\" />\n<p data-start=\"1468\" data-end=\"1495\"><strong data-start=\"1468\" data-end=\"1493\">Storage and Handling:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1496\" data-end=\"1684\">\n<li data-start=\"1496\" data-end=\"1538\">Store lyophilized powder at <strong data-start=\"1526\" data-end=\"1535\">-20°C</strong>.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1539\" data-end=\"1610\">Upon reconstitution, refrigerate at <strong data-start=\"1577\" data-end=\"1586\">2-8°C</strong> and utilize promptly.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1611\" data-end=\"1684\">Always employ aseptic techniques during handling to maintain sterility.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1686\" data-end=\"1689\" />\n<p data-start=\"1691\" data-end=\"1720\"><strong data-start=\"1691\" data-end=\"1718\">Product Specifications:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1721\" data-end=\"1858\">\n<li data-start=\"1721\" data-end=\"1757\"><strong data-start=\"1723\" data-end=\"1734\">Purity:</strong> ≥99% (HPLC Verified)</li>\n<li data-start=\"1758\" data-end=\"1802\"><strong data-start=\"1760\" data-end=\"1775\">Appearance:</strong> Lyophilized white powder</li>\n<li data-start=\"1803\" data-end=\"1858\"><strong data-start=\"1805\" data-end=\"1820\">Solubility:</strong> Fully soluble in bacteriostatic water</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1860\" data-end=\"1863\" />\n<p data-start=\"1865\" data-end=\"2131\"><strong data-start=\"1538\" data-end=\"1557\">Important Note:</strong><br data-start=\"1557\" data-end=\"1560\" />This product is strictly <strong data-start=\"1585\" data-end=\"1610\">FOR RESEARCH USE ONLY</strong> and is intended exclusively for in vitro research and laboratory experimentation by qualified professionals. It is <strong data-start=\"1726\" data-end=\"1733\">not</strong> a drug, food, cosmetic, or dietary supplement, and has not been evaluated by the FDA. This peptide is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. The bodily introduction into humans or animals is strictly prohibited by law. Any mi