 potential roles in:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"1012\" data-end=\"1574\">\n<li data-start=\"1012\" data-end=\"1145\"><strong data-start=\"1014\" data-end=\"1044\">Tissue Repair and Healing:</strong> Investigating effects on cellular proliferation, tissue regeneration, and wound healing processes.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1146\" data-end=\"1296\"><strong data-start=\"1148\" data-end=\"1176\">Gastrointestinal Health:</strong> Studying mechanisms involved in protecting and repairing gastrointestinal tissues, mucosal integrity, and gut health.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1297\" data-end=\"1439\"><strong data-start=\"1299\" data-end=\"1327\">Inflammation Modulation:</strong> Evaluating anti-inflammatory properties and influences on cytokine signaling pathways in experimental models.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1440\" data-end=\"1574\"><strong data-start=\"1442\" data-end=\"1471\">Musculoskeletal Research:</strong> Examining potential impacts on tendon, ligament, and muscle tissue repair, recovery, and regeneration.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1576\" data-end=\"1579\" />\n<p data-start=\"1581\" data-end=\"1608\"><strong data-start=\"1581\" data-end=\"1606\">Storage and Handling:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1609\" data-end=\"1853\">\n<li data-start=\"1609\" data-end=\"1711\">Store tablets or capsules at controlled room temperature (<strong data-start=\"1669\" data-end=\"1680\">15-25°C</strong>) in a dry, dark environment.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1712\" data-end=\"1770\">Protect from moisture and direct exposure to sunlight.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1771\" data-end=\"1853\">Handle according to standard laboratory protocols to maintain product integrity.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1855\" data-end=\"1858\" />\n<p data-start=\"1860\" data-end=\"1889\"><strong data-start=\"1860\" data-end=\"1887\">Product Specifications:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1890\" data-end=\"2090\">\n<li data-start=\"1890\" data-end=\"1926\"><strong data-start=\"1892\" data-end=\"1903\">Purity:</strong> ≥99% (HP