</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"309\" data-end=\"312\" />\n<p data-start=\"314\" data-end=\"846\"><strong data-start=\"314\" data-end=\"330\">Description:</strong><br data-start=\"330\" data-end=\"333\" />Melanotan-2 is a synthetic cyclic peptide analog of alpha-melanocyte-stimulating hormone (α-MSH), extensively studied for its potential to stimulate melanogenesis and influence pigmentation pathways. Research into Melanotan-2 explores diverse physiological processes, including pigmentation enhancement, sexual function modulation, and appetite regulation. Provided as a lyophilized powder, Melanotan-2 supports advanced laboratory research in skin health, melanocortin receptor pathways, and metabolic processes.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"848\" data-end=\"851\" />\n<p data-start=\"853\" data-end=\"942\"><strong data-start=\"853\" data-end=\"879\">Research Applications:</strong><br data-start=\"879\" data-end=\"882\" />Melanotan-2 is actively researched for potential roles in:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"943\" data-end=\"1518\">\n<li data-start=\"943\" data-end=\"1079\"><strong data-start=\"945\" data-end=\"967\">Skin Pigmentation:</strong> Investigating its stimulation of melanin synthesis and protective effects against UV-induced cellular damage.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1080\" data-end=\"1216\"><strong data-start=\"1082\" data-end=\"1108\">Sexual Health Studies:</strong> Examining melanocortin receptor-mediated pathways influencing sexual arousal and physiological responses.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1217\" data-end=\"1347\"><strong data-start=\"1219\" data-end=\"1254\">Appetite and Energy Regulation:</strong> Studying its interactions with energy balance, satiety mechanisms, and metabolic pathways.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1348\" data-end=\"1518\"><strong data-start=\"1350\" data-end=\"1379\">Photoprotection Research:</strong> Evaluating its potential to mitigate UV-related cellular damage and exploring implications for reducing risks associated with UV exposure.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1520\" data-end=\"1523\" />\n<p data-start=\"1525\" data-end=\"1552\"><strong data-start=\"1525\" data-end=\"1550\">Storage and Handling:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1553\" data-end=\"1745\">\n<li data-start=\"1553\" data-end=\"1595\">Store lyophilized powder at <strong data-start=\"1583\" data-end=\"1592\">-20°C</strong>.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1596\" data-end=\"1664\">After reconstitution, refrigerate at <strong data-start=\"1635\" data-end=\"1644\">2-8°C</strong> and use promptly.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1665\" data-end=\"1745\">Maintain aseptic handling practices to ensure sterility and product integrity.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1747\" data-end=\"1750\" />\n<p data-start=\"1752\" data-end=\"1781\"><strong data-start=\"1752\" data-end=\"1779\">Product Specifications:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1782\" data-end=\"1913\">\n<li data-start=\"1782\" data-end=\"1818\"><strong data-start=\"1784\" data-end=\"1795\">Purity:</strong> ≥99% (HPLC Verified)</li>\n<li data-start=\"1819\" data-end=\"1863\"><strong data-start=\"1821\" data-end=\"1836\">Appearance:</strong> Lyophilized white powder</li>\n<li data-start=\"1864\" data-end=\"1913\"><strong data-start=\"1866\" data-end=\"1881\">Solubility:</strong> Soluble in bacteriostatic water</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1915\" data-end=\"1918\" />\n<p data-start=\"1920\" data-end=\"2515\"><strong data-start=\"1920\" data-end=\"1939\">Important Note:</strong><br data-start=\"1939\" data-end=\"1942\" />This product is strictly <strong data-start=\"1967\" data-end=\"1992\">FOR RESEARCH USE ONLY</strong> and is intended exclusively for in vitro research and laboratory experimentation by qualified professionals. It is <strong data-start=\"2108\" data-end=\"2115\">not</strong> a drug, food, cosmetic, or dietary supplement, and has not been evaluated by the FDA. This peptide is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. The bodily introduction into humans or animals is strictly prohibited by law. Any misuse, misbranding, or mislabeling is a violation of federal regulations and may result in legal action under applicable federal, state, or local laws.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"2517\" data-end=\"2520\" />\n<p data-start=\"2522\" data-end=\"2583\"><strong data-start=\"2522\" data-end=\"2537\">References:</strong><br data-start=\"2537\" data-end=\"2540\" />Referenced scientific publications include:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"2585\" data-end=\"2818\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">\n<li data-start=\"2585\" data-end=\"2716\">Hadley, M. E., et al. (1998). <em data-start=\"2617\" data-end=\"2670\">“Melanotan-2: A Novel Approach to Sunless Tanning.”</em> Annals of the New York Academy of Sciences.</li>\n<li data-start=\"2717\" data-end=\"2818\" data-is-last-node=\"\">Wessells, H., et al. (2000). <em data-start=\"2748\" data-end=\"2809\">“Effects of Melanotan-2 on Male Sexual Function in Humans.”</em> Urology.</li>\n</ul>',55.00,24.00,NULL,10.00,'in_stock','active',2,NULL,0,0,0,'https://myoasislabs.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Melanotan-2-scaled.jpg','https://myoasislabs.com/product/melanotan-2-10mg/','2025-12-04 13:37:06','2025-12-05 14:12:57',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,133),(93,'CJC-1295 DAC 5mg','<hr data-start=\"40\" data-end=\"43\" />\n<p data-start=\"45\" data-end=\"72\"><strong data-start=\"45\" data-end=\"70\">Chemical Information:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"73\" data-end=\"418\">\n<li data-start=\"73\" data-end=\"114\"><strong data-start=\"75\" data-end=\"97\">Molecular Formula:</strong> C₁₆₅H₂₆₉N₄₇O₄₆</li>\n<li data-start=\"115\" data-end=\"153\"><strong data-start=\"117\" data-end=\"138\">Molecular Weight:</strong> 3647.2 g/mol</li>\n<li data-start=\"154\" data-end=\"321\"><strong data-start=\"156\" data-end=\"169\">Sequence:</strong> Tyr-D-Ala-Asp-Ala-Ile-Phe-Thr-Gln-Ser-Tyr-Arg-Lys-Val-Leu-Ala-Gln-Leu-Ser-Ala-Arg-Lys-Leu-Leu-Gln-Asp-Ile-Met-Leu-Lys-Lys-Lys-Lys-Lys-Lys-Lys-Lys-Ser</li>\n<li data-start=\"322\" data-end=\"418\"><strong data-start=\"324\" data-end=\"348\">Molecular Structure:</strong> Refer to Certificate of Analysis for detailed structural information.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"420\" data-end=\"423\" />\n<p data-start=\"425\" data-end=\"908\"><strong data-start=\"425\" data-end=\"441\">Description:</strong><br data-start=\"441\" data-end=\"444\" />CJC-1295 (DAC) is a synthetic peptide analog of growth hormone-releasing hormone (GHRH), enhanced with Drug Affinity Complex (DAC) technology to extend its biological half-life. It is extensively studied in laboratory research for its potential effects on endogenous growth hormone secretion, cellular repair mechanisms, and metabolic functions. Provided as a lyophilized powder, CJC-1295 (DAC) maintains optimal stability during storage and research applications.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"910\" data-end=\"913\" />\n<p data-start=\"915\" data-end=\"1024\"><strong data-start=\"915\" data-end=\"941\">Research Applications:</strong><br data-start=\"941\" data-end=\"944\" />Laboratory studies involving CJC-1295 (DAC) commonly explore its potential to:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"1025\" data-end=\"1519\">\n<li data-start=\"1025\" data-end=\"1174\"><strong data-start=\"1027\" data-end=\"1064\">Promote Growth Hormone Secretion:</strong> Investigating prolonged stimulation of growth hormone release for metabolic and cellular function analyses.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1175\" data-end=\"1308\"><strong data-start=\"1177\" data-end=\"1218\">Support Cellular Repair and Recovery:</strong> Researching possible influences on tissue regeneration processes and recovery dynamics.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1309\" data-end=\"1423\"><strong data-start=\"1311\" data-end=\"1338\">Explore Fat Metabolism:</strong> Examining impacts on lipid metabolism and body composition in experimental models.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1424\" data-end=\"1519\"><strong data-start=\"1426\" data-end=\"1455\">Study Endocrine Function:</strong> Evaluating interactions within the hypothalamic-pituitary axis.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1521\" data-end=\"1524\" />\n<p data-start=\"1526\" data-end=\"1553\"><strong data-start=\"1526\" data-end=\"1551\">Storage and Handling:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1554\" data-end=\"1751\">\n<li data-start=\"1554\" data-end=\"1596\">Store lyophilized powder at <strong data-start=\"1584\" data-end=\"1593\">-20°C</strong>.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1597\" data-end=\"1663\">Once reconstituted, refrigerate at <strong data-start=\"1634\" data-end=\"1643\">2-8°C</strong> and use promptly.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1664\" data-end=\"1751\">Utilize aseptic techniques during handling to maintain product sterility and quality.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1753\" data-end=\"1756\" />\n<p data-start=\"1758\" data-end=\"1787\"><strong data-start=\"1758\" data-end=\"1785\">Product Specifications:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1788\" data-end=\"1919\">\n<li data-start=\"1788\" data-end=\"1824\"><strong data-start=\"1790\" data-end=\"1801\">Purity:</strong> ≥99% (HPLC Verified)</li>\n<li data-start=\"1825\" data-end=\"1869\"><strong data-start=\"1827\" data-end=\"1842\">Appearance:</strong> Lyophilized white powder</li>\n<li data-start=\"1870\" data-end=\"1919\"><strong data-start=\"1872\" data-end=\"1887\">Solubility:</strong> Soluble in bacteriostatic water</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1921\" data-end=\"1924\" />\n<p data-start=\"1926\" data-end=\"2521\"><strong data-start=\"1926\" data-end=\"1945\">Important Note:</strong><br data-start=\"1945\" data-end=\"1948\" />This product is strictly <strong data-start=\"1973\" data-end=\"1998\">FOR RESEARCH USE ONLY</strong> and is intended exclusively for in vitro research and laboratory experimentation by qualified professionals. It is <strong data-start=\"2114\" data-end=\"2121\">not</strong> a drug, food, cosmetic, or dietary supplement, and has not been evaluated by the FDA. This peptide is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. The bodily introduction into humans or animals is strictly proh