imentation by qualified professionals. It is <strong data-start=\"2147\" data-end=\"2154\">not</strong> a drug, food, cosmetic, or dietary supplement, and has not been evaluated by the FDA. This peptide is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. The bodily introduction into humans or animals is strictly prohibited by law. Any misuse, misbranding, or mislabeling is a violation of federal regulations and may result in legal action under applicable federal, state, or local laws.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"2556\" data-end=\"2559\" />\n<p data-start=\"2561\" data-end=\"2622\"><strong data-start=\"2561\" data-end=\"2576\">References:</strong><br data-start=\"2576\" data-end=\"2579\" />Referenced scientific publications include:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"2624\" data-end=\"2881\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">\n<li data-start=\"2624\" data-end=\"2761\">Goldstein, A. L., et al. (1991). <em data-start=\"2659\" data-end=\"2715\">“Thymosin Beta-4 and Its Role in Tissue Regeneration.”</em> Annals of the New York Academy of Sciences.</li>\n<li data-start=\"2762\" data-end=\"2881\" data-is-last-node=\"\">Bock-Marquette, I., et al. (2004). <em data-start=\"2799\" data-end=\"2859\">“Thymosin Beta-4 Promotes Angiogenesis and Wound Healing.”</em> Nature Biotechnology.</li>\n</ul>',110.00,46.00,NULL,10.00,'in_stock','active',2,NULL,0,0,0,'https://myoasislabs.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/TB-500-scaled.jpg','https://myoasislabs.com/product/tb-500-10mg/','2025-12-04 13:37:07','2025-12-04 13:37:07',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,87),(106,'Ipamorelin 5mg','<p data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"68\"><strong data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"66\">Chemical Information:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"69\" data-end=\"290\">\n<li data-start=\"69\" data-end=\"106\"><strong data-start=\"71\" data-end=\"93\">Molecular Formula:</strong> C₃₈H₄₉N₉O₅</li>\n<li data-start=\"107\" data-end=\"145\"><strong data-start=\"109\" data-end=\"130\">Molecular Weight:</strong> 711.86 g/mol</li>\n<li data-start=\"146\" data-end=\"193\"><strong data-start=\"148\" data-end=\"161\">Sequence:</strong> Aib-His-D-2-Nal-D-Phe-Lys-NH₂</li>\n<li data-start=\"194\" data-end=\"290\"><strong data-start=\"196\" data-end=\"220\">Molecular Structure:</strong> Refer to Certificate of Analysis for detailed structural information.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"292\" data-end=\"295\" />\n<p data-start=\"297\" data-end=\"859\"><strong data-start=\"297\" data-end=\"313\">Description:</strong><br data-start=\"313\" data-end=\"316\" />Ipamorelin is a selective growth hormone secretagogue peptide widely studied for its targeted stimulation of growth hormone (GH) release via activation of ghrelin receptors. Known for minimal interaction with other hormonal pathways, Ipamorelin is extensively researched in laboratory settings for its potential influence on anabolic processes, cellular recovery, and metabolic function. Provided in lyophilized powder form, Ipamorelin supports advanced research into growth hormone modulation, tissue repair mechanisms, and energy metabolism.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"861\" data-end=\"864\" />\n<p data-start=\"866\" data-end=\"988\"><strong data-start=\"866\" data-end=\"892\">Research Applications:</strong><br data-start=\"892\" data-end=\"895\" />Ipamorelin is actively researched in experimental models to investigate potential roles in:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"989\" data-end=\"1469\">\n<li data-start=\"989\" data-end=\"1119\"><strong data-start=\"991\" data-end=\"1028\">Selective Growth Hormone Release:</strong> Exploring targeted GH secretion pathways with minimized effects on other endocrine axes.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1120\" data-end=\"1240\"><strong data-start=\"1122\" data-end=\"1155\">Cellular Recovery and Repair:</strong> Evaluating effects on tissue healing, regeneration, and cellular repair processes.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1241\" data-end=\"1360\"><strong data-start=\"1243\" data-end=\"1272\">Muscle Anabolism Studies:</strong> Investigating mechanisms of muscle protein synthesis, growth, and anabolic responses.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1361\" data-end=\"1469\"><strong data-start=\"1363\" data-end=\"1388\">Metabolic Regulation:</strong> Studying influences on energy balance, fat metabolism, and metabolic efficiency.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1471\" data-end=\"1474\" />\n<p data-start=\"1476\" data-end=\"1503\"><strong data-start=\"1476\" data-end=\"1501\">Storage and Handling:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1504\" data-end=\"1696\">\n<li data-start=\"1504\" data-end=\"1546\">Store lyophilized powder at <strong data-start=\"1534\" data-end=\"1543\">-20°C</strong>.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1547\" data-end=\"1615\">After reconstitution, refrigerate at <strong data-start=\"1586\" data-end=\"1595\">2-8°C</strong> and use promptly.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1616\" data-end=\"1696\">Maintain aseptic handling practices to ensure sterility and product integrity.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1698\" data-end=\"1701\" />\n<p data-start=\"1703\" data-end=\"1732\"><strong data-start=\"1703\" data-end=\"1730\">Product Specifications:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1733\" data-end=\"1864\">\n<li data-start=\"1733\" data-end=\"1769\"><strong data-start=\"1735\" data-end=\"1746\">Purity:</strong> ≥99% (HPLC Verified)</li>\n<li data-start=\"1770\" data-end=\"1814\"><strong data-start=\"1772\" data-end=\"1787\">Appearance:</strong> Lyophilized white powder</li>\n<li data-start=\"1815\" data-end=\"1864\"><strong data-start=\"1817\" data-end=\"1832\">Solubility:</strong> Soluble in bacteriostatic water</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1866\" data-end=\"1869\" />\n<p data-start=\"1871\" data-end=\"2466\"><strong data-start=\"1871\" data-end=\"1890\">Important Note:</strong><br data-start=\"1890\" data-end=\"1893\" />This product is strictly <strong data-start=\"1918\" data-end=\"1943\">FOR RESEARCH USE ONLY</strong> and is intended exclusively for in vitro research and laboratory experimentation by qualified professionals. It is <strong data-start=\"2059\" data-end=\"2066\">not</strong> a drug, food, cosmetic, or dietary supplement, and has not been evaluated by the FDA. This peptide is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. The bodily introduction into humans or animals is strictly prohibited by law. Any misuse, misbranding, or mislabeling is a violation of federal regulations and may result in legal action under applicable federal, state, or local laws.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"2468\" data-end=\"2471\" />\n<p data-start=\"2473\" data-end=\"2534\"><strong data-start=\"2473\" data-end=\"2488\">References:</strong><br data-start=\"2488\" data-end=\"2491\" />Referenced scientific publications include:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"2536\" data-end=\"2758\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\n<li data-start=\"2536\" data-end=\"2658\">Raun, K., et al. (1998). <em data-start=\"2563\" data-end=\"2621\">“Ipamorelin as a Selective Growth Hormone Secretagogue.”</em> Journal of Endocrinology Research.</li>\n<li data-start=\"2659\" data-end=\"2758\" data-is-last-node=\"\">Smith, R. G., et al. (2005). <em data-start=\"2690\" data-end=\"2740\">“Metabolic and Anabolic Benefits of Ipamorelin.”</em> Peptides Journal.</li>\n</ul>',80.00,23.00,NULL,5.00,'in_stock','active',2,NULL,0,0,0,'https://myoasislabs.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Ipamorelin-scaled.jpg','https://myoasislabs.com/product/ipamorelin-5-mg/','2025-12-04 13:37:07','2025-12-04 13:37:07',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,56),(107,'GHK-Cu 100mg','<p data-start=\"37\" data-end=\"64\"><strong data-start=\"37\" data-end=\"62\">Chemical Information:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"65\" data-end=\"270\">\n<li data-start=\"65\" data-end=\"104\"><strong data-start=\"67\" data-end=\"89\">Molecular Formula:</strong> C₁₄H₂₄N₆O₄Cu</li>\n<li data-start=\"105\" data-end=\"143\"><strong data-start=\"107\" data-end=\"128\">Molecular Weight:</strong> 340.84 g/mol</li>\n<li data-start=\"144\" data-end=\"173\"><strong data-start=\"146\" data-end=\"159\">Sequence:</strong> Gly-His-Lys</li>\n<li data-start=\"174\" data-end=\"270\"><strong data-start=\"176\" data-end=\"200\">Molecular Structure:</strong> Refer to Certificate of Analysis for detailed structural information.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"272\" data-end=\"275\" />\n<p data-start=\"277\" data-end=\"915\"><strong data-start=\"277\" data-end=\"293\">Description:</strong><br data-start=\"293\" data-end=\"296\" />GHK-Cu (glycyl-L-histidyl-L-lysine copper) is a naturally occurring copper peptide extensively studied in laboratory research for its potential roles in tissue remodeling, cellular repair processes, and wound healing. Comprised of three amino acids—glycine, histidine, and lysine—complexed with copper ions, GHK-Cu has been investigated for its capacity to stimulate collagen production, regulate inflammatory pathways, and support skin and hair follicle health. Provided in lyophilized powder form, GHK-Cu is suitable for research into cellular repair mechanisms, dermatological processes, and inflammation modulation.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"917\" data-end=\"920\" />\n<p data-start=\"922\" data-end=\"1024\"><strong data-start=\"922\" data-end=\"948\">Research Applications:</strong><br data-start=\"948\" data-end=\"951\" />Laboratory studies involving GHK-Cu typically explore its potential to:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"1025\" data-end=\"1496\">\n<li data-start=\"1025\" data-end=\"1124\"><strong data-start=\"1027\" data-end=\"1053\">Enhance Wound Healing:</strong> Examine effects on tissue regeneration and cellular repair pathways.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1125\" data-end=\"1251\"><strong data-start=\"1127\" data-end=\"1151\">Support Skin Health:</strong> Investigate its role in collagen synthesis, elasticity, and structural integrity of skin tissues.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1252\" data-end=\"1374\"><strong data-start=\"1254\" data-end=\"1280\">Modulate Inflammation:</strong> Evaluate potential anti-inflammatory effects in both acute and chronic experimental models.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1375\" data-end=\"1496\"><strong data-start=\"1377\" data-end=\"1406\">Stimulate Hair Follicles:</strong> Study effects on hair follicle activity and related mechanisms that may reduce hair loss.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1498\" data-end=\"1501\" />\n<p data-start=\"1503\" data-end=\"1530\"><strong data-start=\"1503\" data-end=\"1528\">Storage and Handling:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1531\" data-end=\"1724\">\n<li data-start=\"1531\" data-end=\"1573\">Store lyophilized powder at <strong data-start=\"1561\" data-end=\"1570\">-20°C</strong>.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1574\" data-end=\"1642\">After reconstitution, refrigerate at <strong data-start=\"1613\" data-end=\"1622\">2-8°C</strong> and use promptly.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1643\" data-end=\"1724\">Maintain aseptic handling procedures to ensure sterility and product integrity.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1726\" data-end=\"1729\" />\n<p data-start=\"1731\" data-end=\"1760\"><strong data-start=\"1731\" data-end=\"1758\">Product Specifications:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1761\" data-end=\"1892\">\n<li data-start=\"1761\" data-end=\"1797\"><strong data-start=\"1763\" data-end=\"1774\">Purity:</strong> ≥99% (HPLC Verified)</li>\n<li data-start=\"1798\" data-end=\"1842\"><strong data-start=\"1800\" data-end=\"1815\">Appearance:</strong> Lyophilized blue powder</li>\n<li data-start=\"1843\" data-end=\"1892\"><strong data-start=\"1845\" data-end=\"1860\">Solubility:</strong> Soluble in bacteriostatic water</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1894\" data-end=\"1897\" />\n<p data-start=\"1899\" data-end=\"2494\"><strong data-start=\"1899\" data-end=\"1918\">Important Note:</strong><br data-start=\"1918\" data-end=\"1921\" />This product is strictly <strong data-start=\"1946\" data-end=\"1971\">FOR RESEARCH USE ONLY</strong> and is intended exclusively for in vitro research and laboratory experimentation by qualified professionals. It is <strong data-start=\"2087\" data-end=\"2094\">not</strong> a drug, food, cosmetic, or dietary supplement, and has not been evaluated by the FDA. This peptide is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. The bodily introduction into humans or animals is strictly prohibited by law. Any misuse, misbranding, or mislabeling is a violation of federal regulations and may result in legal action under applicable federal, state, or local laws.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"2496\" data-end=\"2499\" />\n<p data-start=\"2501\" data-end=\"2562\"><strong data-start=\"2501\" data-end=\"2516\">References:</strong><br data-start=\"2516\" data-end=\"2519\" />Referenced scientific publications include:</p>\n<ul data-start=\"2564\" data-end=\"2845\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\n<li data-start=\"2564\" data-end=\"2732\">Maquart, F. X., et al. (1993). <em data-start=\"2597\" data-end=\"2698\">“Stimulation of Collagen Synthesis in Fibroblast Cultures by the Tripeptide-Copper Complex GHK-Cu.”</em> Journal of Cellular Physiology.</li>\n<li data-start=\"2733\" data-end=\"2845\" data-is-last-node=\"\">Pickart, L., et al. (2008). <em data-start=\"2763\" data-end=\"2814\">“The Human Tripeptide GHK and Tissue Remodeling.”</em> Biomedicine &amp; Pharmacotherapy.</li>\n</ul>',99.00,45.00,NULL,100.00,'in_stock','active',2,NULL,0,0,0,'https://myoasislabs.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/GHK-CU-100MCG-scaled.jpg','https://myoasislabs.com/product/ghk-cu-100mg/','2025-12-04 13:37:07','2025-12-04 13:37:07',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,51),(108,'BPC-157 5mg','<p data-start=\"38\" data-end=\"65\"><strong data-start=\"38\" data-end=\"63\">Chemical Information:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"66\" data-end=\"223\">\n<li data-start=\"66\" data-end=\"105\"><strong data-start=\"68\" data-end=\"90\">Molecular Formula:</strong> C₆₂H₉₈N₁₆O₂₂</li>\n<li data-start=\"106\" data-end=\"145\"><strong data-start=\"108\" data-end=\"129\">Molecular Weight:</strong> 1419.54 g/mol</li>\n<li data-start=\"146\" data-end=\"223\"><strong data-start=\"148\" data-end=\"161\">Sequence:</str