with B12','<div class=\"product-description\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\"><strong>GLP-2TZ Capsules with B12</strong> from <strong>Alpha &amp; Omega Peptide</strong> are formulated for advanced laboratory studies on metabolism and cellular function. This research compound blends <strong>GLP-1 dual analog activity</strong> with <strong>Vitamin B12</strong> to help scientists explore nutrient interaction, peptide stability, and cofactor efficiency. Because it performs reliably, it supports precise testing and clear data collection under controlled lab conditions.</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em 1.5em !important;padding: 0 !important\">\n<li>Advances research on GLP receptor behavior and nutrient absorption.</li>\n<li>Includes Vitamin B12 to enhance metabolic and cellular pathway analysis.</li>\n<li>Delivers a stable capsule format for accurate, repeatable laboratory testing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\"><strong>Important Notice:</strong> This product is for research use only. It is not for human consumption, and dosing instructions are not provided.</p>\n</div>',95.00,NULL,NULL,1.00,'in_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/GLP-2TZ-AO-Capsules.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/glp-2tz-capsules-with-b12/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 14:02:16',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,89),(111,'Orforglipron 6MG  90 Capsules','<div class=\"product-description\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\"><strong>Orforglipron (6MG)</strong> is a first-in-class, small-molecule <strong>GLP-1 receptor agonist</strong> in oral form for investigational and laboratory research. Unlike peptide-based GLP-1 analogs, <strong>Orforglipron</strong> offers an orally bioavailable structure that supports ongoing study of receptor activity, compound stability, and metabolic pathways without peptide formulation limits.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\">Research areas of interest may include:</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em 1.5em !important;padding: 0 !important\">\n<li>Evaluation of glucose regulation mechanisms.</li>\n<li>Study of receptor binding and metabolic signaling.</li>\n<li>Comparison of oral vs. peptide-based GLP-1 analog behavior.</li>\n<li>Exploration of compound structure and bioavailability.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>',239.00,NULL,NULL,6.00,'in_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Orforglipron-Peptide-Capsule-Bottle.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/orforglipron/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 14:02:16',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,90),(112,'Passion and Performance Dissolving Strips','<div class=\"product-description\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\"><strong>Melts™ Passion™ Dissolving Strips</strong> contain a blend of <strong>PT-141</strong>, <strong>Oxytocin</strong>, <strong>Aminophenylpyrrole</strong>, and <strong>Vitamin B3</strong> to support sexual wellness, intimacy, and emotional connection. This balanced formula helps enhance desire and promote overall well-being while staying gentle and easy to use. The fast-dissolving strips provide a discreet, portable, and needle-free option for daily or occasional use. They melt quickly on the tongue, making them perfect for travel or active lifestyles. As a result, users can enjoy a smooth, fast-acting way to support closeness, energy, and vitality wherever they are.</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em 1.5em !important\">\n<li>Encourages desire, connection, and sexual wellness</li>\n<li>Acts quickly in a discreet and easy-to-use format</li>\n<li>Supports natural energy, mood, and overall balance</li>\n</ul>\n</div>',239.99,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Melts™-Passion™-Dissolving-Strips-Tin.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/melts-passion-dissolving-strips/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 14:02:16',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,91),(113,'Vitality Power