li>\n<li>Used in research focused on cell aging, regeneration, and repair</li>\n</ul>\n</div>',33.00,NULL,NULL,10.00,'in_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/epitalon.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/epitalon-10mg/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 14:02:16',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,49),(126,'Copper Glow Anti-Aging Cream','<div class=\"product-description\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\"><strong>Copper Glow Cream</strong> blends two advanced peptides, Snap-8 and GHK-Cu, with deeply hydrating and antioxidant-rich ingredients. Together, they help smooth wrinkles, boost collagen, and bring back a healthy, youthful glow. This formula supports firm, radiant skin while providing lasting moisture and protection.</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em 1.5em !important\">\n<li>Smooths fine lines and helps reduce visible wrinkles</li>\n<li>Boosts collagen for firmer, more resilient skin</li>\n<li>Hydrates deeply and restores a youthful, radiant tone</li>\n</ul>\n</div>',52.00,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_1813.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/copper-glow-anti-aging-cream/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 20:45:38',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,420),(127,'GLP-2TZ 60MG','<div class=\"product-description\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\"><strong>GLP-2TZ</strong> is a dual agonist peptide that targets both the <strong>GLP-1</strong> and <strong>GIP receptors</strong>, offering researchers a reliable tool to study metabolism, energy balance, and glucose regulation. Its dual-receptor activity provides insight into how these pathways interact to influence metabolic health and hormone function.</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em 1.5em !important;padding: 0 !important\">\n<li>Acts on both GLP-1 and GIP receptors for advanced metabolic research.</li>\n<li>Helps explore the link between energy regulation and glucose balance.</li>\n<li>Provides consistent results in controlled laboratory conditions.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>',325.00,NULL,NULL,60.00,'in_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/TIRZ-60-NEW.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/glp-2tz-60mg/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 14:02:16',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,97),(128,'GLP-3RT 24MG','<div class=\"product-description\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\"><strong>GLP-3RT 24MG</strong> replaces our earlier <strong>GLP-3RT 20MG</strong>. <strong>GLP-3RT</strong> is a GGG tri-agonist peptide that works on the <strong>GLP-1</strong>, <strong>GIP</strong>, and <strong>glucagon receptors</strong>. It acts like a standard GLP-1 agonist but also activates the glucagon receptor, giving it a broader range of effects for lab studies.</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em 1.5em !important;padding: 0 !important\">\n<li>Works on GLP-1, GIP, and glucagon receptors for wider research use.</li>\n<li>Supports studies on metabolism, energy balance, and blood sugar control.</li>\n<li>Provides stronger and more complete receptor activity than standard GLP-1 agonists.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>',240.00,NULL,NULL,10.00,'in_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/RETA-24-1.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/glp-3rt-24mg/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 14:02:16',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,101),(129,'CopperCharge – HyperCharge Shampoo','<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"194\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"38\" data-is-only-node=\"\">CopperCharge – HyperCharge Shampoo</strong> is a sulfate-free peptide formula that strengthens follicles, hydrates strands, and restores shine for thicker, healthier-looking hair.</p>',32.00,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Screenshot-2025-08-05-170254.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/coppercharge-hypercharge-shampoo/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-1