,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/BPC-157-10MG.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/bpc-157-10mg/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 14:02:16',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,3),(133,'Tesofensine 500mcg','<div class=\"product-description\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\"><strong>Tesofensine</strong> is an investigational compound that researchers study for its role in weight management. It works by influencing <strong>serotonin</strong>, <strong>norepinephrine</strong>, and <strong>dopamine</strong>, which together help scientists explore how brain signals affect hunger, fullness, and metabolism. As a result, this compound gives research teams a reliable way to study appetite control and energy use. In addition, it is made strictly for research use only.</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em 1.5em !important;padding: 0 !important\">\n<li>Helps researchers understand how neurotransmitters influence hunger and satiety.</li>\n<li>Supports studies on energy balance, metabolism, and appetite regulation for clearer results.</li>\n<li>Furthermore, offers consistent and dependable performance in appetite-related experiments.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>',150.00,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Teso-Tabs.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/tesofensine-500mcg/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 14:02:16',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,78),(134,'Bacteriostatic Water 30ML &#8211; Hospira','<p class=\"ai-optimize-17\"><strong data-start=\"53\" data-end=\"91\">Hospira Brand Bacteriostatic Water</strong> is a sterile solution with 0.9% benzyl alcohol, made under strict GMP standards. Ideal for research, it’s filtered, aseptically packaged, and ensures purity, safety, and reliable results in lab applications.</p>',30.00,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/10-ML.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/bacteriostatic-