arkings for precise liquid preparation.</p>',5.00,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Screenshot-2025-04-30-130541.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/mixing-syringe-21g-10ml-luer-lock/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 14:02:16',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,110),(139,'GLP-2TZ 15MG','<p><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"33\" data-is-only-node=\"\">GLP-2TZ </strong>is a dual agonist peptide targeting<strong> GLP-1</strong> and <strong data-start=\"446\" data-end=\"467\">GIP </strong>receptors, giving scientists a strong tool to study metabolism, energy balance, and blood sugar.  Because it acts on two hormone systems, <strong data-start=\"595\" data-end=\"606\">GLP-2TZ</strong> helps researchers see how dual receptor activity affects metabolic function.</p>',125.00,NULL,NULL,10.00,'out_of_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/TIRZ-15-1.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/glp-2tz-15mg/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 14:02:16',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,97),(140,'CopperCharge Duo – HyperCharge Shampoo &amp; Conditioner','<p data-start=\"83\" data-end=\"138\"><strong data-start=\"83\" data-end=\"136\">CopperCharge Duo – HyperCharge Shampoo &amp; Conditioner &#8211; </strong><strong data-start=\"51\" data-end=\"104\">Simple Sulfate-Free Peptide Shampoo &amp; Conditioner</strong> combines peptides, vitamins, and nourishing botanicals to strengthen, hydrate, and revitalize hair from root to tip. This gentle, sulfate-free duo promotes shine, thickness, and scalp health for stronger, healthier-looking hair every day.</p>',60.00,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/COPPER-CHARGE-SHAMPOO-conditioner-.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/coppercharge-duo-hypercharge-shampoo-conditioner/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 19:20:49',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,416),(141,'GLP-3RT 6MG','<div class=\"product-description\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\"><strong>GLP-3RT 6MG</strong> is a lab-made tri-agonist peptide that works on <strong>GLP-1</strong>, <strong>GIP</strong>, and <strong>glucagon receptors</strong>. Researchers use it to study obesity, metabolism, and heart health. It serves as a reliable tool for exploring how triple-hormone receptor activity affects energy balance and metabolic function in research environments.</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em 1.5em !important;padding: 0 !important\">\n<li>Acts on three main hormone receptors for broad metabolic research.</li>\n<li>Supports studies on energy use, blood sugar control, and fat balance.</li>\n<li>Helps scientists observe how metabolism and heart function connect.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>',75.00,NULL,NULL,6.00,'out_of_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Reta-6mg.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/glp-3rt-6mg/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 14:02:16',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,101),(142,'NA-Semax Amidate','<p class=\"ai-optimize-15\"><strong data-start=\"274\" data-end=\"291\">NA-Semax Amidate</strong> is a synthetic peptide modeled on the structure of adrenocorticotropic hormone (ACTH), studied for its potential role in cognitive science, neuroprotection, and central nervous system research.  <strong data-start=\"274\" data-end=\"291\">NA-Semax Amidate</strong> if often studied for its effects on brain pathways, stress response, and recovery functions, deepening the understanding of brain health, resilience, and adaptation.</p>',55.00,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/NA-SEMAX.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/na-semax-10mg/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 14:02:16',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,112),(143,'GLP-2TZ 30MG','<div class=\"product-description\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\"><strong>GLP-2TZ 30MG</strong> is a dual agonist resea