.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/medicine-diabetes-health-care-concept-close-up-insulin-syringes-table-scaled.jpg','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/insulin-syringes-10-pack/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 14:02:16',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,122),(162,'Cagrilintide 10MG','<div class=\"product-description\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\"><strong>Cagrilintide 10MG</strong> is a long-acting form of <strong>amylin</strong>, a peptide hormone released with insulin that helps control appetite, stomach emptying, and blood sugar. As a research peptide, this compound gives scientists a simple and useful way to study metabolism, fullness, and energy balance in lab settings.</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em 1.5em !important;padding: 0 !important\">\n<li>Works on amylin pathways to help study appetite and energy control.</li>\n<li>Supports research on blood sugar and metabolic balance.</li>\n<li>Delivers steady results for long-term peptide testing.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>',140.00,NULL,NULL,10.00,'in_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/CAGRILINTIDE-10MG-2.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/cagrilintide-10mg/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 19:18:02',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,340),(163,'5-Amino-1MQ Capsules','<p><strong>5-Amino-1MQ Capsules</strong> are high-purity research compounds studied for NNMT inhibition, NAD+ regulation, and their role in metabolic and cellular health.</p>',209.00,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',3,NULL,0,0,0,'https://alphaomegapeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/5-AMINO-CAPSULES.png','https://alphaomegapeptide.com/products/5-amino-1mq-capsules/','2025-12-04 14:02:16','2025-12-04 14:02:16',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,4),(164,'BPC-157 500MCG Capsules','<p data-start=\"2133\" data-end=\"2266\"><strong data-start=\"2133\" data-end=\"2264\">BPC-157 500MCG Capsules – A pharmaceutical-grade peptide in a convenient 60-capsule container for advanced scientific research.</strong></p>\n<ul data-star