Cartalax to learn how it might help with cartilage regeneration, tissue repair, and slowing down problems caused by aging joints. You can buy Cartalax at PureRawz, but only for research use.</span></p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Product Type:</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Peptide</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Product Name:</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Cartalax</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Application:</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Scientific Research</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Molar Mass:</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">333.29 g/mol</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Chemical Formula:</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> C12H19N3O8</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Sequence:</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ala-Glu-Asp</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Synonyms:</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">AED, T-31, SCHEMBL5324601</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">What is Cartalax?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Cartalax is a peptide bioregulator. That means it may help send signals in the body that tell cartilage cells, called chondrocytes, to repair damage and stay strong. It may also help the body make proteins that keep joints smooth and flexible.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Some early research shows that Cartalax might also help lower inflammation, which is when joints feel swollen or sore. If that inflammation is reduced, the cartilage might be less likely to break down. That&#8217;s why Cartalax is being studied to see if it might help with swelling in joints. Scientists also study it with other joint-related peptides.</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">How Does Cartalax Work in the Body of Subjects?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Researchers believe that Cartalax may work by helping to stimulate the natural repair of damaged cartilage cells, also called chondrocytes. It may encourage the production of important proteins that keep joints smooth and mobile. Cartalax might also help reduce inflammation, which can protect the cartilage from further wear and tear. Some lab results suggest it may support joint structure, which is why it&#8217;s of great interest in the study of orthopedic supplements and anti-inflammatory peptides.</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">What is the Scientific Foundation of Cartalax?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Cartalax wasn&#8217;t discovered by accident, it was developed after many years of research by scientists. It was made by the Institute of Bioregulation and Gerontology in St. Petersburg, Russia. This group has worked for decades on understanding how peptides help the body heal and grow tissues.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Cartalax is one of several compounds developed to support specific organs and tissues, making it a focused tool in research about joint health and cartilage repair.</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">What are the Key Benefits of Cartalax Peptide?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Researchers exploring Cartalax are especially interested in how it might help the body repair cartilage, maintain joint function, and support overall mobility. Let&#8217;s break down some examples below:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">May Support Cartilage Repair and Joint Health</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Could Help with Movement and Flexibility in Studies</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">May Reduce Inflammation</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">These benefits come from early research and are meant for informational purposes only.</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Why Choose PureRawz for Cartalax?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Picking the right place to buy research peptides is important. PureRawz stands out because of the quality and care they provide.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tested and Trusted Quality: Every batch of Cartalax is checked in a lab to make sure it is clean and good for research.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Safe Packaging and Fast Shipping: Cartalax comes in secure containers, so it doesn&#8217;t get damaged during delivery. Shipping is fast and reliable, and you&#8217;ll get tracking info to see where your order is.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Great Customer Feedback: PureRawz has been receiving good reviews and feedback from the website and even on social media. The main reason? Quality products and efficient customer service.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">FAQs </span></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">What&#8217;s the best way to store Cartalax peptide?</span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Keep it in a cool place, like a fridge or freezer, to make sure it stays strong and fresh. Avoid heat or sunlight.</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">How is Cartalax packaged for shipping?</span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Cartalax is sealed in airtight, temperature-safe packaging to keep it protected during shipping.</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Can I combine Cartalax with other peptides in studies?</span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Yes, some researchers use Cartalax with other peptides to learn how they work together.</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Does Cartalax come with a Certificate of Analysis?</span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Yes! You can ask for a <a href=\"https://purerawz.co/certificate-of-analysis/\">Certificate of Analysis</a> (COA) that shows how pure the Cartalax is. It&#8217;s also available on the website or from customer service.</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Disclaimer</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Cartalax is only for lab and scientific use. It is not a medicine or supplement. Do not take it by mouth or inject it. It is not approved by the FDA and is not meant to treat or cure any health problems. All information on this page is for learning and research only.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Please read our <a href=\"https://purerawz.co/terms-conditions/\">Terms and Conditions</a>. We recommend doing your own research from reliable sources before buying. If you have questions, email us at </span><a href=\"mailto:support@purerawz.co\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">support@purerawz.co</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">.</span></p>',73.62,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',4,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purerawz.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Cartalax-20mg_PURZ.webp','https://purerawz.co/product/cartalax/','2025-12-04 14:51:09','2025-12-04 14:51:09',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,17),(206,'Testagen','<ul>\n<li>1st and 3rd Party Verified for 99% Purity</li>\n<li>Free Shipping on Orders Over $100+</li>\n</ul>',67.39,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',4,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purerawz.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Testagen-20mg_PURZ.webp','https://purerawz.co/product/testagen/','2025-12-04 14:51:09','2025-12-04 14:51:09',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,6),(207,'Retinalamin','<ul>\n<li>1st and 3rd Party Verified for 99% Purity</li>\n<li>Free Shipping on Orders Over $100+</li>\n</ul>',50.39,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',4,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purerawz.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Retilanamin-10mg_PURZ.webp','https://purerawz.co/product/retilanamin/','2025-12-04 14:51:09','2025-12-04 14:51:09',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,151),(208,'Thyroidget','<ul>\n<li>1st and 3rd Party Verified for 99% Purity</li>\n<li>Free Shipping on Orders Over $100+</li>\n</ul>',174.44,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','