 TRH-R1 in the brain of experimental models, it may modulate different neurochemical pathways. These pathways then influence motor activity, arousal, and neuronal signaling.</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chemical Properties</span></h2>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Pubchem CID</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">114750</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Molecular Formula</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">17</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">23</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">7</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">O</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">5</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Synonyms</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Taltirelin</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">103300-74-9</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">taltireline</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">TA 0910</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">TA-0910</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Molecular Weight</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">405.4 g/mol</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Property</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hygroscopic</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Purity</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&gt;98%</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>HPLC testing</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Verified</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Potential Benefits</b></td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">May enhance central nervous system stimulation as studied by researchers</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Might improve neuroprotective effects in experimental models</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">It might have better stability and bioavailability</span></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>CAS</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">103300-74-9</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Chemical Structure Depiction</b></td>\n<td><img src=\"https://purerawz.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/image2.png\" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>IUPAC</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">(4<em>S</em></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">)-</span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">-[(2</span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">)-1-[(2</span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">)-2-carbamoylpyrrolidin-1-yl]-3-(1</span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">-imidazol-5-yl)-1-oxopropan-2-yl]-1-methyl-2,6-dioxo-1,3-diazinane-4-carboxamide</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Potential Side Effects</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Research studies on various experimental models suggest that the compound may cause gastrointestinal problems and insomnia.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Solubility</b></td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Soluble to 50mM in sterile water</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Handling and Storage of Taltirelin</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Handling and storing Taltirelin is important for long-term research use. Here are the guidelines to follow:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Researchers have suggested that Taltirelin can be stored at -20&deg;C (lyophilized).</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In solution, store at -20&deg;C and use within 1 month to prevent loss of potency. Aliquot to avoid multiple freeze/thaw cycles.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Always reseal the vials promptly to avoid moisture.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Do not expose to a humid environment</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Use carefully in lab settings</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Wear proper gloves and eyewear when dealing with this peptide</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Make sure to check the airport and customs regulations when considering travelling with Taltirelin</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Do not use Taltirelin for research purposes after the expiration date shown on the packaging.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Research Application of Taltirelin</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Taltirelin is being researched by various medical researchers in labs for the following potential applications.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Researchers use Taltirelin to study its potential effects on motor function and neuronal signaling in experimental models.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br />\n</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">A few researchers have used Taltirelin to investigate arousal and central neurotransmitter modulation in preclinical models.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Taltirelin has been explored for its possible protective effects against neuronal damage and oxidative stress in preclinical studies.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Why Choose Purerawz to Buy Taltirelin Online?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">We offer researchers of all levels with authentic first-and third-party tested Taltirelin along with Certificate of Analysis</span><a href=\"https://purerawz.co/certificate-of-analysis/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> (COA)</span></a><span style=\"font-w