hoice for those who appreciate the spirit of the tiger. This magnetic masterpiece features a striking depiction of a fierce tiger, symbolizing strength, resilience, and determination. Whether you place it on your refrigerator, office whiteboard, or any magnetic surface, this magnet embodies the essence of power and confidence.</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>PureRawz Proudly American Magnet</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000\">The PureRawz Proudly American Magnet is a celebration of patriotism and the United States of America. This magnet proudly displays the iconic stars and stripes in our own unique design, making it a perfect addition to your home, office, or any space where you want to express your love for the USA. It&#8217;s not just a magnet; it&#8217;s a statement of pride and unity.</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>PureRawz Eagle Magnet</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000\">The PureRawz Eagle Magnet is a symbol of freedom, majesty, and resilience. Featuring a majestic eagle in flight, this magnet adds a touch of elegance and inspiration to any environment. Whether you&#8217;re a fan of nature&#8217;s beauty or appreciate the symbolism of the eagle, this magnet is a tribute to the indomitable spirit of the wild.</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Why Choose PureRawz Magnets?</strong></span></h2>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Magnet Flux Density and the Power of the North and South Poles</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Magnet flux density, also known as magnetic flux density, is the fundamental measure of the strength and intensity of a magnetic field at a specific point in space. It&#8217;s what sets the north and south poles of magnets in such a way that they attract or repel each other, creating the magnetic magic we all know.</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Premium Quality and Rare Earth Metals</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Our magnets are crafted with the utmost attention to detail and quality. Made from rare earth metals, these magnets exhibit exceptional magnet flux density, making them stronger and more efficient in their magnetic properties.</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Versatile Magnetic Material</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000\">PureRawz Magnets are not just decorative; they are powerful magnetic materials that can be placed on various magnetic surfaces, allowing you to adorn your surroundings with style and personality.</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Express Yourself with Magnetic Moment</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Each magnet in our collection tells a unique story, whether it&#8217;s about strength, patriotism, or freedom. Choose the magnet that resonates with your personality and values, and let it become a part of your magnetic moment.</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Enduring Permanent Magnets</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000\">PureRawz Magnets are not just ordinary; they are permanent magnets designed to maintain their magnetic flux density over time. This means your magnet will continue to display its magnetic properties, making it a long-lasting statement piece.</span></p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>The Influence of External Magnetic Fields</strong></span></h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000\">While PureRawz Magnets maintain their magnetic moment, they are also influenced by external magnetic fields. As you place them in your space, they interact with the magnetic field around them, adding an intriguing dimension to your environment.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Magnet flux density is what makes the magnetic field around a magnet so fascinating, and PureRawz Magnets bring this magnetic phenomenon to life. Whether you choose PureRawz Ace The Tiger, PureRawz USA, or PureRawz Eagle, you&#8217;re not just decorating; you&#8217;re making a magnetic statement that truly reflects your style and identity.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000\">Make your space uniquely yours with PureRawz Magnets today. Choose from our collection, and let magnet flux density become a part of your everyday life, enhancing the magnetic magic that surrounds you.</span></p>\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Disclaimer</strong></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000\">This information is for educational purposes only and does not constitute medical advice. THE PRODUCTS DESCRIBED HEREIN ARE FOR LABORATORY AND RESEARCH USE ONLY. All clinical research must be conducted with oversight from the appropriate Institutional Review Board (IRB). All preclinical research must be conducted with oversight from the appropriate Institutional Animal Care and Use Committee (IACUC) following the guidelines of the Animal Welfare Act (AWA).</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000\">Our content is intended to be used and must be used for informat</span>ional purposes only. It is very important to do your own analysis and research from Trusted Sources before making any purchase, based on your personal circumstances. You should independently research and verify any information that you find on our Website and wish to rely upon.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>By completing and paying for your order, you agree to our Terms and Conditions. Customer satisfaction is our number one priority &ndash; if you are not 100% satisfied with the product you received, please contact us at support@purerawz.co</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong>ATTENTION: All our products are for LABORATORY AND RESEARCH PURPOSES ONLY, not for veterinary or human usage.</strong></div>',2.99,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',4,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purerawz.co/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Purerawz-Magnets-3-1.jpeg','https://purerawz.co/produc