ders Over $100+</li>\n</ul>',57.10,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',4,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purerawz.co/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/C3G-20-Extract-60tabs_Purz.webp','https://purerawz.co/product/c3g/','2025-12-04 14:51:10','2025-12-04 14:51:10',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,204),(267,'Ethanol 99.5% Denatured (Ethyl Alcohol)','<h2>Ethanol Denatured 99.5% (Ethyl Alcohol) &#8211; Product Details</h2>\n<p>Ethanol, also known as ethyl alcohol, is a clear, colorless, and volatile liquid with a distinctive odor. While it can react assertively with metals, producing hydrogen, and can explosively react with potent oxidizing agents, it finds diverse applications, from school chemistry labs to substance or chemical testing.</p>\n<p>Our Ethanol Denatured 99.5% undergoes meticulous processing to adhere to stringent standards, ensuring both sterility and injection-grade quality, making it a reliable choice for various purposes.</p>\n<h2><b>What is Ethanol 99.5%?</b></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ethanol 99.5% has the following essential properties:</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chemical safety: Flammable</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Molecular formula: C2H6O or CH3CH2OH</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Synonyms: Grain alcohol, ethyl alcohol, 64-17-5</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Refractive index: 1.3611 at 20 degrees Celsius</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Natural sources of ethanol include the fermentation of carbohydrates by yeasts or petrochemical processes like ethylene hydration. It has modern medicinal uses as an antiseptic, disinfectant, a solvent for some drugs, and an antidote for methanol and ethylene glycol toxicity, in addition to its historical usage as a general anesthetic.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">When alcoholic beverages (beer, wine, and spirits) are diluted, ethanol is present. It is used topically to prevent skin infections in pharmaceutical preparations (such as rubbing compounds, lotions, tonics, and colognes), cosmetics, and perfumes.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ethanol is a high-purity substance used as an industrial solvent for fats, oils, waxes, resins, and hydrocarbons and may be present in fuels labeled as ethanol-blended fuels.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Many chemical compounds are made from it, including lacquers, plastics and plasticizers, rubber and rubber accelerators, aerosols, mouthwash products, soaps and cleaning preparations, polishes, surface coatings, dyes, inks, adhesives, preservatives, pesticides, explosives, petrol additives/substitutes, elastomers, antifreeze, yeast growth medium, human and veterinary medicines, and dehydrating agents.</span></p>\n<h2><b>Potential Applications of Ethanol 99.5%</b></h2>\n<h3><b>Ethanol 99.5% and Personal Care Products</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Numerous cosmetics and beauty products frequently contain ethanol as an ingredient. It functions as an astringent to aid in cleaning the skin, as a preservative in lotions to prevent the separation of the ingredients, and to aid in the adhesion of hairspray to the hair. [</span><a href=\"https://www.chemicalsafetyfacts.org/chemicals/ethanol/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Alcohol, a common component in many hand sanitizers, is effective in killing microorganisms like bacteria, fungi, and viruses. [</span><a href=\"https://www.chemicalsafetyfacts.org/chemicals/ethanol/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h3><b>Ethanol 99.5% and Household Products</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">An efficient solvent for use in paints, lacquers, and varnish, as well as personal care and home cleaning products, ethanol mixes easily with water and many organic compounds. Because it effectively eliminates organisms that could endanger consumers, ethanol is added to cleaning products as a preservative. [</span><a href=\"https://www.chemicalsafetyfacts.org/chemicals/ethanol/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Specially denatured 40 B 200 proof alcohol is used as a solvent for various cleaning solutions, including household detergents, theater sprays, incense, and room deodorants.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ethanol 99.5% is effective in cleaning different parts of structures, such as a kitchen counter, handrails, hard floors, etc.</span></p>\n<h3><b>Ethanol 99.5% and Food Industry</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">As a food additive, ethanol is widely utilized. To end the fermentation process at the desired time, for instance, ethanol is added to port, sherry, and other southern wines &#8211; the so-called fortification. [</span><a href=\"https://www.itwreagents.com/italy/en/product/ethanol+absolute,+99,5%+for+synthesis/161086\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">With a few exceptions, these liqueurs and wines have a high residual sugar content and are, therefore, very sweet due to the premature termination of fermentation. Other foods can be preserved by adding ethanol. [</span><a href=\"https://www.itwreagents.com/italy/en/product/ethanol+absolute,+99,5%+for+synthesis/161086\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h3><b>Ethanol 99.5% and Medicine</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Iodine tincture is made by combining iodine with ethanol for wound disinfection, and potassium iodide is added to stop hydrogen iodide from forming. Ethanol serves as the solvent in this process. [</span><a href=\"https://www.itwreagents.com/italy/en/product/ethanol+absolute,+99,5%+for+synthesis/161086\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Percutaneous ethanol injection therapy (PEI therapy), which involves the use of 95% or pure ethanol, can be used to treat circumscribed tumors like hepatocellular carcinoma and &#8220;hot&#8221; thyroid nodules (also percutaneous ethanol injection therapy). [</span><a href=\"https://www.itwreagents.com/italy/en/product/ethanol+absolute,+99,5%+for+synthesis/161086\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">If a drug is or is not soluble in water, ethanol may be used as a solvent, co-solvent, or solubilizer in liquid form. Water and ethanol mix easily together. It plays a crucial role in stabilizing and preserving liquid herbal medicines. [</span><a href=\"https://www.itwreagents.com/italy/en/product/ethanol+absolute,+99,5%+for+synthesis/161086\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h3><b>Ethanol as Fuel</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The majority of time, ethanol is added to conventional fuel in concentrations of 5% (E5 as an admixture in regular vehicle gasoline) or 85%. (as E85 for vehicles suitable for this purpose). [</span><a href=\"https://www.itwreagents.com/italy/en/product/ethanol+absolute,+99,5%+for+synthesis/161086\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Commercial fuel cells run on hydrogen, methanol, or natural gas that has been reformatted. Due to its widespread availability, low cost, excellent purity, and minimal toxicity, ethanol is a desirable alternative. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Numerous fuel cell designs have entered testing, such as direct ethanol fuel cells, auto-thermal reforming systems, and thermally integrated systems. [</span><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1016/j.apenergy.2015.02.002\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h2><b>Safety and Side Effects</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Exposure to ethanol vapors in high concentrations can irritate the eyes, skin, and respiratory system and lead to ataxia, sleepiness, narcosis (stupor or unconsciousness), poor coordination, and impaired perception.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Additionally, it can lead to decreased inhibitions, lightheadedness, shallow breathing, unconsciousness, and even death. Ingestion, inhalation, and skin absorption of ethanol are all harmful.</span></p>\n<h2><b>Frequently Asked Questions</b></h2>\n<h3><b>What are the different grades of ethanol?</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Clinical research of specific medications and substances has been conducted using ethanol, among its many industrial applications. It is utilized for biomolecule purification and precipitation, histology specimen staining and restoration, tissue dehydration before embedding, and disinfection. Three types of ethanol are frequently used in laboratories.</span></p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">95% ethanol: This is the highest ethanol concentration available for laboratory studies.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Absolute ethanol (99 &#8211; 100%): This grade is widely used as a synthetic organic chemistry and chromatography reagent. Absolute ethanol readily absorbs water.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Denatured ethanol: This kind of ethanol is exempt from several beverage taxes because it doesn&#8217;t contain additives that make it harmful to drink, including methanol and isopropanol. It is, therefore, less expensive than pure ethanol.</span></li>\n</ol>\n<h3><b>How is ethanol different from isopropyl alcohol?</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Although ethanol and isopropyl alcohol are both tiny molecules, they are comparable except for where the alcohol group is located on their chemical structures. Both types of alcohol may be intended as disinfectants and both are combustible.</span></p>\n<h3><b>What does ethanol 99.5 denatured mean?</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Denatured alcohol is typically denaturized with at least 5% methanol and can include between 70 and 99 percent ethyl alcohol. Denatured ethanol is free from federal alcohol excise taxes for approved end uses, even if it is unfit to drink.</span></p>\n<h3><b>How is ethanol 99.5 made available?</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This high-impact alcohol, which has a purity of 99.5 ethanol, may come as alcohol packaged safely for the intended purposes of the buyers. It could be offered via a contract price or a list price by its authorized sellers.</span></p>\n<h3><b>Where can you buy ethanol 99.5%?</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><a href=\"https://purerawz.co/\">Pure Rawz</a> is the best place to buy the highest-quality ethanol 99.5 online. Our current USA gallon pack stock of 99.5% ethanol is made in the USA. Visit our website for more laboratory-grade solutions that you may use for your research studies.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In order to be the best supplier of research chemicals, we provide our customers with reference materials for every product they purchase. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">All of our products come with an independent, third-party-issued <a href=\"https://purerawz.co/certificate-of-analysis/\">Certificate of Analysis</a> for identification, purity, and concentration.</span></p>\n<h2>Disclaimer</h2>\n<div>\n<div>This information is for educational purposes only and does not constitute medical advice. THE PRODUCTS DESCRIBED HEREIN ARE FOR LABORATORY AND RESEARCH USE ONLY.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>All clinical research must be conducted with oversight from the appropriate Institutional Review Board (IRB). All preclinical research must be conducted with oversight from the appropriate Institutional Animal Care and Use Committee (IACUC) following the guidelines of the Animal Welfare Act (AWA).</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Our content is intended to be used and must be used for informational purposes only. It is very important to do your own analysis and research from Trusted Sources before making any purchase, based on your personal circumstances. You should independently research and verify any information that you find on our Website and wish to rely upon.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>By completing and paying for your order, you agree to our <a href=\"https://purerawz.co/terms-conditions/\">Terms and Conditions</a>. Customer satisfaction is our number one priority. If you are not 100% satisfied with the product you received, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:support@purerawz.co\">support@purerawz.co</a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong>ATTENTION: All our products are for LABORATORY AND RESEARCH PURPOSES ONLY, not for veterinary or human usage.</strong></div>\n</div>',12.60,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',4,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purerawz.co/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Ethanol-995-1.webp','https://purerawz.co/product/ethanol-99-5-denatured-ethyl-alcohol-solvent/','2025-12-04 14:51:10','2025-12-04 14:51:10',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,205),(268,'Benzyl Benzoate USP Grade &#8211; Solvent','<h2>Benzyl Benzoate USP Grade &#8211; Product Details</h2>\n<p>Carefully processed to meet rigorous standards for sterility and injection-grade quality, our Benzyl Benzoate USP Grade is a versatile organic compound. Recognized for its potential applications as both a medication and insect repellent, it has shown efficacy in treating scabies and lice. Moreover, it occurs naturally in Peruvian balsam, Tolu balsam, and various flowers.</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Benzyl benzoate finds application in the world of perfumery since it can promote the stability and odor characteristics of the main ingredients of the product. Certain studies claim benzyl benzoate could be a safe ingredient among cosmetic products (but further studies are needed to verify this). [</span><a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29243541/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Even though benzyl benzoate may offer promising effects, this chemical may still irritate delicate skin.</span></p>\n<h2><b>What is Benzyl Benzoate?</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Benzyl Benzoate is a synthetic and naturally occurring chemical used as a fragrance ingredient/aroma compound, artificial flavor in the food industry, cosmetic additive, preservative, and solvent in today&#8217;s market. It is a benzyl alcohol and benzoic acid ester.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Benzyl Benzoate is a dye carrier and a solvent for cellulose derivatives. It is also used as a polymer and cellulose plasticizer. However, benzyl benzoate is not listed as an active ingredient. It enhances the suspension, stability, and odor of the main ingredients.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Benzyl Benzoate is found naturally in Peruvian balsam, Tolu balsam, and cinnamon essential oil. It has a weak, sweet-balsamic odor, forming either a colorless oily liquid or solid flakes. It is found naturally in various blossoms (e. g. tuberose and hyacinth).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">It is on the World Health Organization&#8217;s List of Essential Medicines, which lists the most critical medications required in a basic health system. It is also effective against chiggers, ticks, and mosquitoes. It is a safe, effective, and inexpensive topical treatment for human scabies. For treating human scabies, lotions and anti-aging creams for adults may contain up to 25% benzyl benzoate concentration.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">For treatment in children, concentrations are diluted to 10% &#8211; 12.5%.</span></p>\n<h2><b>Possible Applications of Benzyl Benzoate</b></h2>\n<h3><b>Benzyl Benzoate may be used to treat scabies</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Recent research has shown that Benzyl Benzoate is effective in the treatment of permethrin-resistant crusted scabies and in combination with ivermectin in patients who have relapsed after a single ivermectin treatment. In developing countries where resources are scarce, it is used to treat scabies as a less expensive alternative. [</span><a href=\"https://academic.oup.com/pmj/article/81/951/7/7031861\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h3><b>Benzyl Benzoate may be helpful as head lice treatment</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">For more than 60 years, benzyl benzoate, an ester of benzoic acid and benzyl alcohol initially extracted from natural products like balsam of Peru, has been used to treat head lice infestations. Although several treatment plans have been used, two to three applications on consecutive days have been advised. [</span><a href=\"https://wchh.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/pdf/10.1002/psb.179\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The main adverse effect of benzyl benzoate is skin irritation, which often appears minutes after application and can occasionally be so severe that it requires rapid rinsing off to relieve. It is not advised to be used on children since the dilution required to lessen its irritating effect on youngsters may also lessen its effectiveness. [</span><a href=\"https://wchh.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/pdf/10.1002/psb.179\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h3><b>Benzyl Benzoate, an active fragrance ingredient</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Benzyl benzoate frequently appears in the fragrance industry, either as a natural element of the essential oils used in the scent or as a synthetic ingredient used as a fixative to help preserve the longevity of a smell. [</span><a href=\"https://ifrafragrance.org/standards/IFRA_STD_009.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h2><b>How Does Benzyl Benzoate Work?</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Benzyl benzoate, a compound that is both a synthetic and a natural chemical, has a toxic effect on the parasite&#8217;s nervous system, causing it to die. It is also toxic to mite eggs, though the exact mechanism is unknown. Benzyl benzoate has been shown in vitro to kill the Sarcoptes mite in 5 minutes.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">As a fragrance, benzyl benzoate can give a product a balsamic scent. It can also be used as a solvent with other fragrances to help them dissolve into the mixture. Benzyl benzoate also acts as a fixative in scented products, slowing the escape of other fragrances and increasing the fragrance&#8217;s life span.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Benzyl benzoate can be a plasticizer when added to more solid products such as soaps. A plasticizer makes a product less brittle, allowing it to be bent and squished more before snapping or crumbling.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">To date, several high-end and drug store brands utilize Benzyl Benzoate in their cosmetics and personal care formulations.</span></p>\n<h2><b>Safety and Side Effects</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">There is a chance that benzyl benzoate will cause an allergic reaction.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">It can irritate the skin and cause it to become red, dry, and itchy. More serious side effects, such as loss of consciousness and jerking movements, are usually only seen at much higher concentrations than in cosmetic products.</span></p>\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What is benzyl benzoate used for in cosmetics?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Benzyl alcohol, benzoic acid and its salts, and benzyl benzoate are primarily used in cosmetic products as fragrance ingredients/preservatives. It could be present among personal care formulations such as creams, aftershave lotion, and scalp products.</span></p>\n<h3>Is benzyl benzoate a natural compound?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Benzyl benzoate occurs naturally in various plants. Depending on the product, this natural component can serve as a fixative, a scent, a solvent, a plasticizer, a preservative, and more in cosmetic items.</span></p>\n<h3>Where can you buy benzyl benzoate?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><a href=\"https://purerawz.co/\">Pure Rawz</a> is the best place to buy the highest-quality <strong>benzyl benzoate online</strong>.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In order to be the best supplier of research chemicals, we provide reference materials with every product we sell. All of our products come with an independent, third-party-issued <a href=\"https://purerawz.co/certificate-of-analysis/\">Certificate of Analysis</a> for identification, purity, and concentration.</span></p>\n<h2>Disclaimer</h2>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div>This information is for educational purposes only and does not constitute medical advice. THE PRODUCTS DESCRIBED HEREIN ARE FOR LABORATORY AND RESEARCH USE ONLY.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>All clinical research must be conducted with oversight from the appropriate Institutional Review Board (IRB). All preclinical research must be conducted with oversight from the appropriate Institutional Animal Care and Use Committee (IACUC) following the guidelines of the Animal Welfare Act (AWA).</div>\n<div>Our content is intended to be used and must be used for informational purposes only. It is very important to do your own analysis and research from Trusted Sources before making any purchase based on your own personal circumstances. You should independently research and verify any information that you find on our Website and wish to rely upon.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>By completing and paying for your order, you agree to our <a href=\"https://purerawz.co/terms-conditions/\">Terms and Conditions</a>. Customer satisfaction is our number one priority, if you are not 100% satisfied with the product you received, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:support@purerawz.co\">support@purerawz.co</a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong>ATTENTION: All our products are for LABORATORY AND RESEARCH PURPOSES ONLY not for veterinary or human usage.</strong></div>\n</div>',12.60,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',4,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purerawz.co/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Benzyl-Benzoate-1.webp','https://purerawz.co/product/benzyl-benzoate-usp-grade-solvent/','2025-12-04 14:51:10','2025-12-04 14:51:10',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,206),(269,'Benzyl Alcohol USP Grade &#8211; Solvent','<h2>Benzyl Alcohol USP Grade &#8211; Product Details</h2>\n<p>Benzyl alcohol, commonly referred to as benzyl alcohol NF, is an organic aromatic alcohol utilized in the production of various chemicals. Recognized for its mild and pleasant aromatic odor, this liquid finds applications in diverse fields, such as head lice treatment. Our Benzyl Alcohol USP Grade undergoes meticulous processing to adhere to stringent standards, guaranteeing both sterility and injection-grade quality, making it a reliable choice for your specific needs.</p>\n<h2>What is Benzyl Alcohol USP Grade &#8211; Solvent?</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The colorless liquid known as benzoyl alcohol has a light, pleasant aroma. Its polarity, low toxicity, and low vapor pressure make it a proper solvent. Benzyl alcohol is completely miscible in alcohols and only partially soluble in water (4 g/100 mL).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In producing other benzyl compounds, benzyl alcohol is a preservative in many injectable drugs and cosmetics and a flavoring and fragrance ingredient. It is an organic aromatic alcohol found in many fruits, teas, and essential oils like Ylang-Ylang, Jasmine, and Hyacinth.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Possible Applications of Benzyl Alcohol USP Grade-Solvent</h2>\n<h3>Benzyl Alcohol USP Grade &#8211; Solvent for Industrial Use</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Inks, waxes, shellacs, paints, lacquers, and epoxy resin coatings all use benzyl alcohol as a general solvent. As a result, it can be used in paint strippers, particularly when combined with compatible viscosity enhancers, to encourage the mixture to adhere to painted surfaces. [</span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Benzyl_alcohol\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">It improves the dyeing of wool, nylon, and leather as a dye solvent. [</span><a href=\"https://books.google.com.ph/books?id=XZ2QB7bu5LwC&amp;pg=PA487&amp;redir_esc=y#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h3>Benzyl Alcohol USP Grade -Solvent for Food and Beverages</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Benzyl alcohol may function as a flavoring agent for certain foods and drinks. Because it lengthens food goods&#8217; shelf lives, the food and beverage industry frequently uses it. [</span><a href=\"https://www.echemi.com/cms/777105.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h3>Benzyl Alcohol USP Grade &#8211; Solvent in Healthcare</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Benzyl alcohol is used as a bacteriostatic preservative in intravenous medications, cosmetics, and topical drugs at low concentrations. Caution is advised if a high percentage of Benzyl alcohol is used as benzaldehyde is formed when benzyl alcohol is used as a preservative in an injectable formulation solution. [</span><a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21828928/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">As the active ingredient in lotion shampoo containing 5% benzyl alcohol, it effectively treats lice infestations. [</span><a href=\"https://dailymed.nlm.nih.gov/dailymed/drugInfo.cfm?setid=5754f979-32b7-4406-a3a9-ed36aac6a37a\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What personal care products use benzyl alcohol USP grade?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Benzyl alcohol and benzyl benzoate are used in a wide variety of personal care products: hair, nail, bath products, soaps, detergents, eye products, shaving products, cosmetics, etc. It is a cosmetic product that complies with cosmetics directives and observes good manufacturing practices and is safe to use.</span></p>\n<h3>Where can you buy benzyl alcohol USP grade?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Pure Rawz is the best place to buy the highest-quality benzyl alcohol USP online.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Pure Rawz also offers research chemicals, such as</span><a href=\"https://purerawz.co/product-category/peptides/\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400\">peptides</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> and</span><a href=\"https://purerawz.co/product-category/nootropics/\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400\">nootropics</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, that licensed researchers may use for their clinical studies.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In order to be the best supplier of research chemicals, we provide reference materials with every product we sell. All of our products come with an independent, third-party-issued <a href=\"https://purerawz.co/certificate-of-analysis/\">Certificate of Analysis</a> for identification, purity, and concentration.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Disclaimer</h2>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div>This information is for educational purposes only and does not constitute medical advice. THE PRODUCTS DESCRIBED HEREIN ARE FOR LABORATORY AND RESEARCH USE ONLY.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>All clinical research must be conducted with oversight from the appropriate Institutional Review Board (IRB). All preclinical research must be conducted with oversight from the appropriate Institutional Animal Care and Use Committee (IACUC) following the guidelines of the Animal Welfare Act (AWA).</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Our content is intended to be used and must be used for informational purposes only. It is very important to do your own analysis and research from Trusted Sources before making any purchase, based on your personal circumstances. You should independently research and verify any information that you find on our website and wish to rely upon.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>By completing and paying for your order, you agree to our <a href=\"https://purerawz.co/terms-conditions/\">Terms and Conditions</a>. Customer satisfaction is our number one priority. If you are not 100% satisfied with the product you received, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:support@purerawz.co\">support@purerawz.co</a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong>ATTENTION: All our products are for LABORATORY AND RESEARCH PURPOSES ONLY, not for veterinary or human usage.</strong></div>\n</div>',12.01,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',4,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purerawz.co/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Benzyl-Alcohol-USP-Grade-60ml-1.webp','https://purerawz.co/product/benzyl-alcohol-usp-grade-solvent/','2025-12-04 14:51:10','2025-12-04 14:51:10',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,207),(270,'DMSO Dimethyl Sulfoxide &#8211; Solvent','<h2>DMSO Dimethyl Sulfoxide (USP Grade) &#8211; Product Details</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">DMSO (Dimethyl sulfoxide) is a clear, odorless chemical in liquid form that is produced cheaply as a by-product of the paper industry. It is widely available as a solvent in the United States, but the FDA currently limits its medical use to specific experimental applications, including the palliative treatment of interstitial cystitis. Our DMSO is carefully processed to meet rigorous standards, ensuring sterility and injection-grade quality</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Its pharmaceutical grade is under investigation as a potential medication and dietary supplement. Based on studies about dimethyl sulfoxide liquid, it can be taken orally, administered topically to the skin, or injected into the veins (used intravenously or by IV). However, proper precautions are advised because this chemical might lead to skin irritation.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">DMSO could have other applications to treat bladder inflammation (interstitial cystitis), limb pain caused by an injury (complex regional pain syndrome), and intravenous (IV) medication leakage into surrounding skin and tissue (extravasation).</span></p>\n<p><b>Chemical dietary supplements of DMSO are also being studied to treat other diseases; however, there is little scientific evidence to back up most of these claims.</b></p>\n<h2><b>What is DMSO Dimethyl Sulfoxide?</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In the United States, dimethyl sulfoxide (DMSO) has been utilized for over a century. It is a natural substance derived from wood pulp that is safe to use when appropriately utilized.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">DMSO is a colorless, non-synthesized liquid derived from lignin, a natural component that keeps tree cells together. The melting point of DMSO is 189 degrees Celsius (372.2 degrees Fahrenheit). This extraction occurs during the manufacturing of wood pulp, and the DMSO is then naturally processed for use in various applications, and sold as a solvent in particular proportions.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">It is a highly polar organic liquid widely used as a chemical solvent. Because of its ability to penetrate biological membranes, it is used as a vehicle for pharmaceutical and topical applications.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">It&#8217;s also used to keep tissue safe during cryopreservation. Dimethyl sulfoxide has a pharmacological activity that includes analgesia and anti-inflammation. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">DMSO became popular as one of the natural remedies available and a topical pain reliever for pulled, strained, and sprained muscles and joints in the late 1960s.</span></p>\n<h2><b>Possible Applications of DMSO Dimethyl Sulfoxide</b></h2>\n<h3><b>DMSO Dimethyl Sulfoxide and Inflammation</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In patients with arthritis and connective tissue injuries, dermal application of DMSO appears to provide rapid, temporary pain relief. [</span><a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/3916302/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">However, claims of anti-inflammatory effects or faster healing are currently unsubstantiated. [</span><a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/3916302/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h3><b>DMSO Dimethyl Sulfoxide and Arthritis</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">According to new double-blind research, after three weeks a 25% dosage of DMSO in gel form reduced osteoarthritis pain much better than a placebo, . DMSO appears to alleviate pain by suppressing the transmission of pain messages via nerves rather than mending injured joints. [</span><a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/3916302/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h3><b>DMSO Dimethyl Sulfoxide and Cancer</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">There has also been some research investigating the benefits of DMSO in suppressing cancer cells. A specific study published in the Journal of Medical Discovery in 2020 discovered evidence of benefit. Despite such promising outcomes, research in this field is just getting started, so many more studies must be conducted before any conclusions can be drawn. [</span><a href=\"https://www.proquest.com/openview/06527232a660b6867effa2ff8f68deed/1?pq-origsite=gscholar&amp;cbl=2050635\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h2><b>Mechanisms of Action</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The mechanism of action of dimethyl sulfoxide is not well understood. In specific biological settings, dimethyl sulfoxide has shown antioxidant activity. Dimethyl sulfoxide, for example, is thought to have a cardiovascular protective effect in copper-deficient rats via an antioxidant mechanism. It is also believed that dimethyl sulfoxide&#8217;s anti-inflammatory activity stems from antioxidant activity.</span></p>\n<h2><b>Safety and Side Effects of DMSO Dimethyl Sulfoxide</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Adverse reactions to DMSO are common, but they are usually minor and are related to the DMSO concentration in the medication solution.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">As a result, the most common side effects include skin rash and pruritus following dermal application, intravascular hemolysis following intravenous infusion, and gastrointestinal discomfort following oral administration. DMSO is not advisable for human use. Buy DMSO for research purposes only.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">You should avoid contact with DMSO in your eyes. Immediately flush eyes with running for 15 minutes. Remember that in using DMSO, it is the sole responsibility of the user to exercise precaution in order to avoid any untoward incidents.</span></p>\n<h2><b>Frequently Asked Questions</b></h2>\n<h3><b>Is DMSO dimethyl sulfoxide safe?</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Dimethyl sulfoxide (DMSO) is still being investigated for its purported health benefits. We recommend using this product for research studies only.</span></p>\n<h3><b>What does DMSO dimethyl sulfoxide smell like?</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Within a few minutes of administering dimethyl sulfoxide to the bladder, you may experience a garlic-like taste. This effect could last several hours. It may also leave a garlic-like odor on your breath and skin for up to 72 hours.</span></p>\n<h3><b>How should you store DMSO?</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The freezing point of DMSO is 18.5°C (65.4°F). The recommended storage room temperature range is 15-30°C. Because this product is sensitive to light, it should be stored in a light-resistant container.</span></p>\n<h3><b>Does DMSO come in a crystal state?</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Yes, DMSO can be purchased in a crystal state. If the product is in a crystal state, place it in a wide container or pot filled with hot (not boiled) water and close it completely if possible. The water level should not rise above the bottle&#8217;s neck. After 30-60 minutes, replace the hot water with a hot one. The bottle should thereafter be kept at a temperature above the melting point.</span></p>\n<h3><b>Where can you buy DMSO?</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><a href=\"https://purerawz.co/\">Pure Rawz</a> is the best place to buy the highest-quality DMSO online. Our website contains product reviews from our current customers. Aside from DMSO, we also offer</span><a href=\"https://purerawz.co/product-category/sarms/\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400\">SARMS</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> and</span><a href=\"https://purerawz.co/product-category/nootropics/\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400\">nootropics</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> for your research studies.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In order to be the best supplier of research chemicals, we provide reference materials with every product we sell. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">All of our products come with an independent, third-party-issued <a href=\"https://purerawz.co/certificate-of-analysis/\">Certificate of Analysis</a> for identification, purity, and concentration.</span></p>\n<h2>Disclaimer</h2>\n<div>This information is for educational purposes only and does not constitute medical advice. THE PRODUCTS DESCRIBED HEREIN ARE FOR LABORATORY AND RESEARCH USE ONLY.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>All clinical research must be conducted with oversight from the appropriate Institutional Review Board (IRB). All preclinical research must be conducted with oversight from the appropriate Institutional Animal Care and Use Committee (IACUC) following the guidelines of the Animal Welfare Act (AWA).</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Our content is intended to be used and must be used for informational purposes only. It is very important to do your own analysis and research from Trusted Sources before making any purchase, based on your personal circumstances. You should independently research and verify any information that you find on our Website and wish to rely upon.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>By completing and paying for your order, you agree to our <a href=\"https://purerawz.co/terms-conditions/\">Terms and Conditions</a>. Customer satisfaction is our number one priority. If you are not 100% satisfied with the product you received, please contact us at support@purerawz.co</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong>ATTENTION: All our products are for LABORATORY AND RESEARCH PURPOSES ONLY, not for veterinary or human usage.</strong></div>',12.60,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',4,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purerawz.co/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/DMSO-Dimethyl-Sulfoxide-60ml-1.webp','https://purerawz.co/product/dmso-dimethyl-sulfoxide-solvent/','2025-12-04 14:51:10','2025-12-04 14:51:10',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,208),(271,'Ethyl Oleate USP Grade &#8211; Solvent','<h2>Ethyl Oleate USP Grade &#8211; Product Details</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ethyl Oleate USP is a pharmaceutical-grade ester created by the condensation of fatty acid, oleic acid, and ethanol. It has an ester value of 95 to 105%. Our Ethyl Oleate USP Grade is carefully processed to meet rigorous standards, ensuring sterility and injection-grade quality.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">It is a colorless to pale light yellow straw color liquid that is clear. After consuming alcohol, human bodies naturally produce ethyl oleate.</span></p>\n<p><b>Ethyl oleate USP for sale is still considered an experimental compound meaning it is not safe for human consumption. Buy this product for research studies only.</b></p>\n<h2>What is Ethyl Oleate USP Grade?</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ethyl Oleate is a fatty acid formed when oleic acid and ethanol combine. Ethyl oleate has also been identified as a honeybee primer pheromone and is produced naturally by our bodies. Its synonym is oleic acid ethyl ester.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ethyl Oleate is used in many applications, including industrial, medical, food, perfume, cosmetics, health, and beauty preparations. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ethyl oleate can be used as a solvent, a glossing agent, and an emollient. It is both an excellent solvent and a good moisturizer used in skin care, hair care, and colour cosmetics.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">It is also used as a fragrance ingredient in household products, such as some Clorox products.</span></p>\n<h2>Possible Applications of Ethyl Oleate USP Grade</h2>\n<h3>Ethyl Oleate USP Grade and Pregnancy</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">For some couples to be able to become pregnant, fertility treatments have to be used. Many of the main pharmaceutical companies&#8217; hormone therapies are based on sesame oil. However, there may be times when sesame oils are in short supply, and certain people may be allergic to specific oils. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">As a result, groups of researchers are investigating the use of Ethyl Oleate to generate daily doses of progesterone in fertility treatments and other hormone replacement therapy applications. [</span><a href=\"https://bmcpregnancychildbirth.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/s12884-018-2002-z\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h3>Ethyl Oleate USP Grade and Steroids</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Steroids and other lipophilic medicines can be dissolved in ethyl oleate. It has characteristics similar to almond oil and peanut oil. It does, however, have the advantage of being less viscous than fixed oils and hence more swiftly absorbed by bodily tissues. [</span><a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/0378517383901254\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h3>Other Known Potential Uses</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ethyl oleate, according to current research, is an effective solvent for active compounds in ointments, creams, and lotions. It can be used as an excipient in transdermal delivery systems to increase the penetration of active compounds. This ester works well as a vehicle or diluent for a wide range of active and inert substances, and it can be used in place of mineral or vegetable oils. [</span><a href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/pdf/10.3109/10717544.2013.879355\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The Food and Drug Administration regulates ethyl oleate as a food additive. Ethyl oleate oral intake has been thoroughly investigated, and due to quick breakdown in the digestive tract, it looks safe for oral ingestion. [</span><a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9252525/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h2>Safety and Side Effects</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Currently, ethyl oleate is thought to be low in toxicity. However, it should not be consumed. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">It has been discovered that this experimental chemical causes minimal tissue irritation.</span></p>\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>Is ethyl oleate safe?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">This solution is inadvisable for human consumption because more research is needed to determine its complete mechanisms of action and how it interacts with the human body.</span></p>\n<p><b>Purchase ethyl oleate for research purposes only.</b></p>\n<h3>Does ethyl oleate occur naturally?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The chemical is produced naturally by the human body following alcohol consumption.</span></p>\n<h3>Where can you buy ethyl oleate?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Pure Rawz is the best place to buy the highest quality ethyl oleate USP grade online.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Aside from this solution, Pure Rawz also sells</span><a href=\"https://purerawz.co/product-category/sarms/\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400\">SARMs</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> and</span><a href=\"https://purerawz.co/product-category/peptides/\"> <span style=\"font-weight: 400\">peptides</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> that are safe to use for laboratory trials and research studies.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In order to be the best supplier of research chemicals, we provide reference materials with every product we sell. All of our products come with an independent, third-party-issued <a href=\"https://purerawz.co/certificate-of-analysis/\">Certificate of Analysis</a> for identification, purity, and concentration.</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong>Disclaimer</strong></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div>This information is for educational purposes only and does not constitute medical advice. THE PRODUCTS DESCRIBED HEREIN ARE FOR LABORATORY AND RESEARCH USE ONLY.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>All clinical research must be conducted with oversight from the appropriate Institutional Review Board (IRB). All preclinical research must be conducted with oversight from the appropriate Institutional Animal Care and Use Committee (IACUC) following the guidelines of the Animal Welfare Act (AWA).</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Our content is intended to be used and must be used for informational purposes only. It is very important to do your own analysis and research from Trusted Sources before making any purchase, based on your personal circumstances. You should independently research and verify any information that you find on our Website and wish to rely upon.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>By completing and paying for your order, you agree to our <a href=\"https://purerawz.co/terms-conditions/\">Terms and Conditions</a>. Customer satisfaction is our number one priority. If you are not 100% satisfied with the product you received, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:support@purerawz.co\">support@purerawz.co</a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong>ATTENTION: All our products are for LABORATORY AND RESEARCH PURPOSES ONLY, not for veterinary or human usage.</strong></div>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',18.01,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',4,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purerawz.co/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Ethyl-Oleate-USP-Grade-60ml-1.webp','https://purerawz.co/product/ethyl-oleate-usp-grade-solvent/','2025-12-04 14:51:10','2025-12-04 14:51:10',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,209),(272,'Echinacea Purpurea Cichoric Acid 2%','<ul>\n<li>1st and 3rd Party Verified for 99% Purity</li>\n<li>Free Shipping on Orders Over $100+</li>\n</ul>',19.22,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',4,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purerawz.co/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Echinacea-27tabs_Purz.webp','https://purerawz.co/product/echinacea-purpurea-cichoric-acid/','2025-12-04 14:51:10','2025-12-04 14:51:10',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,210),(273,'3 5 Diiodo L-Thyronine (T2)','<h2>3 5 Diiodo L-Thyronine T2 &#8211; Product Details</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thyroid hormones (THs) from the thyroid gland are essential endocrine elements that play vital biological roles, such as governing energy metabolism and body weight.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">A known thyroid hormone (TH) derivative 3, 5-diiodo-L-thyronine (or 3,5-T2), is found in biological fluids and significantly affects energy metabolism. 3,5-T2 increases the metabolic rate, cold tolerance, and lipid metabolism among animal models. [</span><a href=\"https://www.karger.com/Article/FullText/491620\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The thyroid controls metabolism, and thyroid hormone derivatives are expected to mimic thyroid hormone regulation, 3,5 T-2 included. The hormone under consideration is also believed to affect mitochondrial fatty acid oxidation. [</span><a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19116374/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Although 3 5 diiodo l-thyronine could promote thyroid hormone metabolism and its alleged medical beneficial effects, this chemical is still considered a research compound. 3 5 diiodo l-thyronine is inadvisable for human consumption.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Pure Rawz sells this product for research purposes only.</span></p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"301\">T2 3,5-diiodo-L-thyronine</td>\n<td width=\"301\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"301\">CAS Number</td>\n<td width=\"301\">1041-01-6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"301\">Molar Mass</td>\n<td width=\"301\">525,077 g/mol</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"301\">Chemical Formula</td>\n<td width=\"301\">C15H13I2NO4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"301\">IUPAC Name</td>\n<td width=\"301\">(2S)-2-amino-3-[4-(4-hydroxyphenoxy)-3,5-diiodophenyl]propanoic acid</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>What is 3 5 Diiodo L-Thyronine T2?</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">3 5 diiodo l-thyronine T2 is an endogenous derivative of thyroid-stimulating hormone that has been proposed to regulate energy expenditure, resting metabolic rate, and hepatic oxygen consumption via a mechanism involving mitochondrial function activation.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">It significantly reduces body fat accumulation in overweight rats fed a high-fat diet (HFD), a risk factor for developing an inflammatory state and related metabolic diseases.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The chemical, as a thyroid-stimulating hormone, also stimulates thyroid-sensitive tissues. A study among Wistar rats from 3 to 6 months of age seems to prove this characteristic of 3,5 diiodo l-thyronine. [</span><a href=\"https://joe.bioscientifica.com/view/journals/joe/221/3/415.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h2>Possible Applications of 3 5 Diiodo L-Thyronine T2</h2>\n<h3>3 5 Diiodo L-Thyronine T2 may help in body weight loss</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Akin to other thyroid hormones, T2 is allegedly capable of affecting weight loss.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The thyroid hormone derivative can increase energy expenditure and prevent high-fat diet-induced obesity and metabolic dysfunction. Most 3 5 diiodo l-thyronine research has focused on the liver and skeletal muscle. [</span><a href=\"https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0116498\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Given the importance of brown adipose tissue (BAT) in energy and metabolic homeostasis, researchers investigated whether 3 5 diiodo l-thyronine could activate BAT thermogenesis. [</span><a href=\"https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0116498\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Indeed, the discovery of functional BAT in adult humans and its essential role in energy metabolism and potential control of triglyceride clearance and glucose disposal suggests that T2 may be able to prevent metabolic dysfunction and related diseases in humans. [</span><a href=\"https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0116498\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Furthermore, 3 5 diiodo l-thyronine may aid in weight loss during caloric restriction (i.e., dieting). [</span><a href=\"https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0116498\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In another study on two healthy individuals, an 8-day 3,5-T2 dose-escalation protocol increased resting metabolic rate. It decreases body weight with no changes or adverse effects on serum thyroid stimulating hormone (TSH), thyroid hormone (TH), thyroid and cardiac function, blood pressure, or serum metabolic parameters such as glycemia, total cholesterol, and triglycerides. [</span><a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4272399/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">] [</span><a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22217997/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><b>Even though 3,5-T2 could help with weight loss management, this experimental compound still requires large-scale clinical trials before becoming a prescribed fat-burning compound.</b></p>\n<h3>3 5 Diiodo L-Thyronine T2 ameliorates diabetic neuropathy</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thyroid function has been examined through the kinetics of glucose-induced insulin secretion from the isolated perfused rat pancreas. [</span><a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/939192/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T2 was found to prevent a significant decrease in SIRT1 protein expression and activity, as well as increases in blood glucose, urine albumin excretion, matrix expansion, transforming growth factor-1 expression, fibronectin, and type IV collagen deposition in diabetic kidneys. [</span><a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0925443913000379\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T2 had similar effects in cultured rat mesangial cells (RMC) exposed to high glucose, which could be reversed by sirtinol, a known SIRT1 inhibitor. [</span><a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0925443913000379\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">These findings suggested that T2 was a protective agent against renal damage in diabetic neuropathy, with an action that involved SIRT1 regulation. [</span><a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0925443913000379\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><b>Despite the alleged effects observed, 3,5 diiodo l thyronine is not a recommended form of cure for diabetic neuropathy. More safe and approved human trials are required here.</b></p>\n<h3>3 5 Diiodo L-Thyronine T2 may prevent diet-induced insulin resistance</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T2, by activating SIRT1, sets off a chain of events that improves the serum lipid profile, prevents fat accumulation, and averts diet-induced insulin resistance. [</span><a href=\"https://diabetesjournals.org/diabetes/article/60/11/2730/33450/Nonthyrotoxic-Prevention-of-Diet-Induced-Insulin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><b>Nevertheless, the outcome of the stated research cannot be treated as conclusive. More tests are needed.</b></p>\n<h3>3 5 Diiodo L-Thyronine T2 may lessen the oxidative capacity</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Long-term T2 treatment promotes visceral adipose lipolysis via HSL activation and effects on adipocyte morphology (observable after two weeks and persistent after 4 weeks), tissue vascularization, and proteins involved in lipid storage and oxidative stress. [</span><a href=\"https://www.readcube.com/articles/10.3389/fendo.2021.703170\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The current study&#8217;s findings indicate that T2 is effective in combating inflammation and oxidative stress caused by a long-term high-fat diet in rats. [</span><a href=\"https://www.readcube.com/articles/10.3389/fendo.2021.703170\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">]</span></p>\n<h2>How Does 3 5 Diiodo L-Thyronine T2 Work?</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">3,5-Diiodo-L-thyronine (3,5-T2) is a metabolite of thyroid hormone. In cell-free assays, it binds to thyroid hormone receptors 1 (TR1), 1 (TR1), and 2 (EC50s = 0.8, 0.79, and 0.1 M, respectively).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Two 3,5-T2 (1 pM) increases oxygen consumption in perfused livers isolated from rats with sodium iodide-induced hypothyroidism.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">When administered to animal models at a dose of 2.5 g/g per day, it reduces subcutaneous and epididymal fat mass and serum leptin and cholesterol levels without affecting body weight in high-fat diet-induced obese mice.</span></p>\n<h2>Safety and Side Effects</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T2 has been shown in obese mice to produce signs of thyrotoxicosis while decreasing body weight and blood glucose levels.</span></p>\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What does 3 5 diiodo l-thyronine do?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T2 was discovered to be a molecule capable of increasing the metabolic rate of hypothyroid rats. It can also reduce adiposity, serum triglyceride, cholesterol levels, liver fat content (steatosis), and body weight gain without reducing calorie/fat intake when given to rats for four weeks, in conjunction with a high-fat diet.</span></p>\n<h3>How do we measure TSH levels?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The TSH test determines the concentration of thyroid-stimulating hormones in your blood. Typical test results range from 0.4 to 4.0 mIU/L.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">If your TSH level is higher than 2.0 mIU/L, you risk developing hypothyroidism. Weight gain, fatigue, depression, and brittle nails and hair are all common symptoms.</span></p>\n<h3>Is 3 5 diiodo l-thyronine for sale safe?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Although the synthetic chemical under consideration holds promising benefits, the studies on it are still insufficient. Thus, 3 5 diiodo l-thyronine for sale should not be used for human consumption but for research purposes only.</span></p>\n<h3>Where can you buy 3 5 diiodo l-thyronine?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Pure Rawz is the best place to buy the highest-quality 3 5 diiodo l-thyronine. Our online store offers many research chemicals, such as</span><a href=\"https://purerawz.co/product-category/peptides/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> peptides</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> and</span><a href=\"https://purerawz.co/product-category/nootropics/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> nootropics</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, that you could use for scientific study purposes.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">In order to be the best supplier of research chemicals, we provide reference materials with every product we sell. All of our products come with an independent, third-party-issued <a href=\"https://purerawz.co/certificate-of-analysis/\">Certificate of Analysis</a> for identification, purity, and concentration.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">We offer free international shipping on all orders above $100. You can pay for your purchase through various methods, including PayPal and Bitcoin. We sell liquid, powder, and capsule high-quality TUDA formulations. All the formulations are equally high-quality.</span></p>\n<div>\n<h2>Disclaimer</h2>\n<p>This information is for educational purposes only and does not constitute medical advice. THE PRODUCTS DESCRIBED HEREIN ARE FOR LABORATORY AND RESEARCH USE ONLY. All clinical research must be conducted with oversight from the appropriate Institutional Review Board (IRB). All preclinical research must be conducted with oversight from the appropriate Institutional Animal Care and Use Committee (IACUC) following the guidelines of the Animal Welfare Act (AWA).</p>\n<p>Our content is intended to be used and must be used for informational purposes only. It is very important to do your own analysis and research from Trusted Sources before making any purchase, based on your personal circumstances. You should independently research and verify any information that you find on our Website and wish to rely upon.</p>\n<p>By completing and paying for your order, you agree to our <a href=\"https://purerawz.co/terms-conditions/\">Terms and Conditions</a>. Customer satisfaction is our number one priority. If you are not 100% satisfied with the product you received, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:support@purerawz.co\">support@purerawz.co</a></p>\n<p><strong>ATTENTION: All our products are for LABORATORY AND RESEARCH PURPOSES ONLY, not for veterinary or human usage</strong>.</p>\n</div>',61.91,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',4,NULL,0,0,0,'https://pure