ll Infuser 2&#8243;','<h2>Purerawz Stainless Steel Tea Ball</h2>\n<h2>ABOUT THIS ITEM</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tea Ball Size: 2&#8243; Diameter</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Secure latch and chain attachment</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Reusable stainless steel design</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ideal for loose herbs and teas</span></p>\n<h2>Tea Origin</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The benefits of tea were only known by the Chinese for many years, but eventually, tea drinking became popular throughout Asia and then the rest of the world. Tea was carried by traders who considered it a popular item, travelers who found daily tea comforting on lengthy travels and scholars and monks who recognized tea&#8217;s mind-soothing and alerting qualities. Tea was a common meditation tool used by Buddhist monks who propagated the discipline throughout Southeast Asia. The first European city to experience tea was Amsterdam. Tea reached London, becoming a staple of British culture and social life. The instruments used to make tea changed along with the popularity of tea. [</span><a href=\"https://books.google.com/books?hl=en&amp;lr=&amp;id=3vXPAgAAQBAJ&amp;oi=fnd&amp;pg=PT10&amp;dq=Tea+Ball+history&amp;ots=n0StqAYcoc&amp;sig=sbAAORdHYE4LNHLzok4A51RToQw\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">] Stainless steel tea ball strainers are an inventive way to replace single-use tea bags with a reusable option. </span></p>\n<h2>Stainless Steel Tea Ball</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Harry Brearley invented the first stainless steel, sometimes known as &#8220;rustless&#8221; steel 1913. This innovation revolutionized the metallurgical sector. [</span><a href=\"https://books.google.com/books?hl=en&amp;lr=&amp;id=3vXPAgAAQBAJ&amp;oi=fnd&amp;pg=PT10&amp;dq=Tea+Ball+history&amp;ots=n0StqAYcoc&amp;sig=sbAAORdHYE4LNHLzok4A51RToQw\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">] Many rust-resistant kitchen tools were created after this discovery, providing an alternative to traditional bamboo utensils. One such creation was the tea ball made of stainless steel. A stainless steel tea ball enhances the pleasure of drinking tea by allowing loose-leaf tea to expand and release its unique scents fully.</span></p>\n<h2>Advantages of Stainless Steel Tea Ball</h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Reusable: Stainless steel tea balls are inexpensive in the long run since they can be reused.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Complete flavor extraction: The stainless steel tea balls allow loose tea leaves to open up, improving flavor extraction.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Environmentally friendly: By opting for a reusable stainless steel tea ball, you reduce the waste generated from single-use disposable tea bags.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>FAQ</h2>\n<h3>How do you use a stainless steel tea infuser?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Fill a tea infuser with loose tea. Steep loose-leaf tea in hot water after closing the infuser and rotating the tea ball to ensure water circulation through the leaves. Use the infuser to steep tea fo2 2-5 minutes to release flavors.</span></p>\n<h3>How do you clean a stainless steel tea ball?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Disassemble your Stainless Steel Tea Ball to clean all parts. First, rinse it in warm water to remove loose tea leaves, then soak it in warm, soapy water to dissolve stubborn residue. If stubborn stains remain, use a soft brush or a vinegar-baking soda mixture or soak it in vinegar. Rinse and dry the filter to prevent mold.</span></p>\n<h3>Is it wrong to brew tea on a stainless steel infuser?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">While some have noted a metallic aftertaste when utilizing stainless steel, it is essential to note that different grades of stainless steel impart different tastes. Some of the cheaper brands could cause this reaction. For this reason, you should only purchase stainless steel tea balls from trusted suppliers, such as Purerawz.</span></p>\n<h3>Loose-leaf tea brewing: disposable tea bags or stainless steel infusers?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Disposable empty tea bags are not as good an alternative as a stainless steel tea ball if you want to thoroughly enjoy your tea at home. With tea infusers, loose tea leaves may fully expand, improving flavor extraction and yielding a robust flavor. Moreover, they may be reused, making them more economical and environmentally beneficial. </span></p>\n<h3>Is there any disadvantage to using Stainless Steel tea Infusers?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">One drawback of tea steeper balls is that delicate tea leaves may escape through larger pores in some designs, ruining the brewing experience. Furthermore, thoroughly cleaning stainless steel tea balls might be a pain, particularly if tiny tea leaves get entangled in the mesh. Fine holes are incorporated into the tea strainer ball infuser mesh from PureRawz to ensure the tea does not escape. However, PureRawz also provides </span><b>disposable tea bags</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> as a substitute option if you would rather skip cleaning.</span></p>\n<h3>Where can I buy a high-quality Stainless Steel Tea Ball for sale?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><a href=\"https://purerawz.co/\">PureRawz</a> offers the safest, most eco-friendly, and highest-quality Stainless Steel Tea Ball. If you are looking for a Stainless Steel Tea Ball near your area, we deliver to all locations worldwide. Register or log in to our website to access a range of promotional discounts and exceptional deals on our Stainless Steel Tea Ball.</span></p>',6.58,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',4,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purerawz.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Screenshot-2023-06-08-at-11.11.32-1.webp','https://purerawz.co/product/stainless-steel-tea-ball-infuser-2/','2025-12-04 14:51:10','2025-12-04 14:51:10',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,315),(394,'Shipping Insurance','<p>Shipping Insurance covers full replacement of the purchased product if lost or damaged during transit. For packages over $150, this will require a signature or replacement of the product will not be granted.</p>',7.35,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',4,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purerawz.co/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/dreamstime_m_2065192-1.jpg','https://purerawz.co/product/shipping-insurance/','2025-12-04 14:51:10','2025-12-04 14:51:10',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,317),(395,'Viking 1 (GHRP-2 + GHRP-6 + Sermorelin)','<ul>\n<li>1st and 3rd Party Verified for 99% Purity</li>\n<li>Free Shipping on Orders Over $100+</li>\n</ul>',147.03,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',4,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purerawz.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Viking-1_Peptide_PURZ.webp','https://purerawz.co/product/viking/','2025-12-04 14:51:10','2025-12-04 14:51:10',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,318),(396,'Digital LCD Diamond Scale 20Grams x 0.001g','<h2>PureRawz Digital LCD Pocket Scale 10g/20g/50g</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The new Purerawz digital LCD pocket scale offers a sophisticated design. We offer a clear protective cover that ensures durability and functionality. Our scale is ideal for accurately weighing powders for your research needs. It can also be used for weighing diamonds, platinum, gold, silver, herbs, medications, and more. Purerawz scale features multiple weighing modes, such as gram, carat, pennyweight and grain. The backlit LCD display makes readings clear and simple. While the tare and add-up functions enhance usability.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Upon receipt, the Purerawz scale is immediately usable due to its pre-calibration. Efficient and safe operation is guaranteed by the auto power-off feature after 1 minute and the overload indicator. The compact design and shock-proof cover make it great for use while travelling.</span></p>\n<h3>Specifications:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Color: Silver</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Measurement Units: gram (g), carat (ct), pennyweight (dwt), grain (gn)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Capacity and Precision: Options for 10g with 0.001g accuracy or 20g capacity</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Batteries: This requires 2 AAA batteries</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Dimensions: 11.5 cm x 6.6 cm x 3.5 cm (4.5 in x 2.6 in x 1.4 in)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Weight of Scale: 57 grams (2.0 oz)</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Included in the package:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">1pc Pocket scale</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">1pc Pair of forceps</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">1pc Calibration weight (10g)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">1pc Calibration weight (5g)</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">1pc User manual</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How to use a digital scale ?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Press the power button to turn on the scale.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Wait for the scale to initialize and display zero.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Calibrate the scale as needed. Calibration weights are included.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Place the item to be weighed on the center.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">If you are using powder or chemicals to be measured, follow this instruction below:</span>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Before weighing powders or other chemicals, use an empty container on the scale.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">To reset the display to zero, press the tare button.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Add the powder or chemical to the container and read the net weight on the display.</span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">After 1 minute of inactivity, the scale turns off to save battery life.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>FAQ</h2>\n<h3>What is a digital pocket scale series used for?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">A digital LCD mini scale is a compact device that is used to precisely measure the weight of small objects. It can also be used in weighing diamonds and other jewelry. In research, it is used for the precise measurement of powders and chemicals. In cookery, it can be a digital kitchen scale to measure ingredients. For personal use, it weighs medications and herbs.</span></p>\n<h3>How to reset a digital pocket weight scale ?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The power button, &#8220;zero,&#8221; &#8220;tare,&#8221; or &#8220;reset&#8221; may set the digital scale to zero, depending on the model. For Purerawz digital LCD pocket scale, just press tare to reset.</span></p>\n<h3>How do you know if your scale is accurate?</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">You can see how accurate your scale is by putting a known weight on it to compare its accuracy. With test weights included for calibration, PureRawz electronic scale makes testing accuracy easier. It is also important to buy a scale that has already been tested and calibrated. Which is something that PureRawz guarantees with our pre-calibration offer.</sp