15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,348),(457,'PNC-27','<p>PNC-27 is a synthetic peptide containing a p53 tumor suppressor protein fragment linked to a membrane-disrupting domain. It is supplied in lyophilized powder form to ensure high purity and stability. PNC-27 is intended strictly for controlled in-vitro laboratory research by qualified professionals. It is not approved for human or veterinary use.</p>',79.00,NULL,NULL,5.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Pnc-27-Product-Featured.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/pnc-27/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,281),(458,'Thymalin','<p>Thymalin is a synthetic peptide originally derived from thymus gland extracts. It is used in laboratory research to explore peptide interactions related to immune system regulation and cellular equilibrium. This compound is supplied in lyophilized powder form and is intended solely for in vitro use by qualified research professionals.</p>',19.00,NULL,NULL,5.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Thymalin-product-img.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/thymalin/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,46),(459,'FOXO4-DRI','<p>FOXO4-DRI is a synthetic peptide engineered in a D-retro-inverso configuration based on a FOXO4 interaction domain. The retro-inverso design and D-residue composition are used in research to study peptide stability and target-interaction modeling in vitro. Supplied as a lyophilized powder, FOXO4-DRI is intended strictly for controlled laboratory research.</p>',99.00,NULL,NULL,5.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/FOXO4-DRI-Product-Featured-image.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/foxo4-dri/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 20:52:07',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,386),(460,'KLOW','<p>KLOW is a proprietary research peptide blend composed of BPC-157, GHK-Cu, TB-500, and KPV. Each peptide represents a distinct structural and functional class of research compound, combined in lyophilized form for advanced laboratory studies. This blend is supplied exclusively for in vitro use and is intended for qualified research professionals.</p>',139.00,NULL,NULL,10.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Klow-image.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/klow/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,349),(461,'Humanin','<p>Humanin is a synthetic peptide corresponding to a mitochondrial-derived bioactive sequence. It is provided in lyophilized powder form to ensure stability and purity for laboratory work. Humanin is designed exclusively for controlled in vitro use and is intended for qualified research professionals studying peptide stability, receptor binding, and signaling pathways.</p>',51.00,NULL,NULL,5.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Humanin-Featured.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/humanin/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,99),(462,'Cartalax','<p>Cartalax is a synthetic tripeptide consisting of alanine, glutamic acid, and aspartic acid. It is provided in lyophilized powder form to ensure stability and high purity for laboratory research. Cartalax is designed exclusively for in-vitro studies carried out by qualified professionals exploring peptide signaling and regulation.</p>',31.00,NULL,NULL,10.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Cartalax-Featured.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/cartalax/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,17),(463,'KPV','<p>KPV is a synthetic tripeptide representing the C terminal sequence of alpha melanocyte-stimulating hormone (α MSH). This compound is supplied as lyophilized powder and intended solely for in vitro laboratory research use by qualified professionals.</p>',29.00,NULL,NULL,5.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/KPV.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/kpv/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,30),(464,'GLP-2 (SU)','<p>GLP-2 (SU), also known as Survodutide (BI 456906), is a long acting investigational peptide engineered to act as a dual agonist at both glucagon-like peptide 1 receptors (GLP 1R) and glucagon receptors (GCGR). A C18 fatty acid acylation prolongs half-life by promoting reversible albumin binding. This agent is supplied as a lyophilized powder, intended exclusively for in vitro laboratory research use.</p>',101.00,NULL,NULL,10.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/GLP-2-SU.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/glp2-su/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,350),(465,'PEG-MGF','<p>PEG-MGF is a pegylated synthetic peptide provided exclusively for in vitro laboratory research in controlled experimental settings. This material is intended solely for investigation of molecular pathways and cellular mechanisms by qualified research professionals with appropriate institutional credentials. It is supplied in lyophilized powder form for analytical and reference purposes only. Any implications regarding biological activity or therapeutic potential are strictly limited to controlled laboratory research models.</p>',34.00,NULL,NULL,2.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/PEG-MGF.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/peg-mgf/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,221),(466,'VIP','<p>Vasoactive Intestinal Peptide (VIP) is a 28 residue synthetic peptide, part of the glucagon/secretin superfamily. It is commonly used in laboratory research to examine peptide ligand interactions and receptor-based cellular responses. VIP is supplied as a lyophilized powder and is intended exclusively for in vitro use by qualified research professionals.</p>',49.00,NULL,NULL,5.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/VIP-product-img-Updated.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/vip/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,337),(467,'Adipotide','<p>Adipotide is a synthetic peptidomimetic designed to target specific receptors on the vasculature of white adipose tissue, delivering a pro-apoptotic signal to fat-specific blood vessels. The sequence includes D-amino acids for improved resistance to proteolytic degradation and selectivity. This compound features two disulfide bridges that contribute to its structural stability in research environments. Adipotide is supplied in lyophilized powder form and intended strictly for in vitro laboratory use.</p>',42.00,NULL,NULL,5.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Adipotide-Product-img.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/adipotide/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,324),(468,'Sermorlin','<p>Sermorlin is a synthetic peptide analog of growth hormone-releasing hormone (GHRH) that consists of the first 29 amino acids of native human GHRH. It has been studied for its ability to stimulate the release of endogenous growth hormone (GH) by acting on the anterior pituitary. Sermorlin is provided in lyophilized powder form for use in research related to endocrine function, growth hormone dynamics, and cellular regeneration.</p>',34.00,NULL,NULL,5.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Sermorelin.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/sermorlin/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,73),(469,'GLP-1 (C)','<p>GLP-1 (C) is a synthetic peptide analog provided in lyophilized powder form for use in qualified laboratory environments. It is commonly used in in vitro systems to explore structural stability, receptor interaction modeling, and peptide pathway evaluation in controlled, non-clinical research settings.</p>',115.00,NULL,NULL,10.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/GLP-1-C.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/glp-1-c/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,351),(470,'GHPR-2','<p>GHPR-2 (Growth Hormone Releasing Peptide-2) is a synthetic hexapeptide that stimulates the secretion of growth hormone (GH) through its interaction with ghrelin receptors. It has been widely studied for its role in promoting anabolic processes, improving energy balance, and supporting tissue repair. GHPR-2 is provided in lyophilized powder form, specifically for research applications related to growth hormone regulation, metabolism, and cellular regeneration.</p>',21.00,NULL,NULL,5.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/GHRP-2.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/ghpr-2/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,352),(471,'CJC-1295 (DAC)/Ipamorelin','<p>This research blend combines <strong>CJC-1295 with DAC</strong>, a long-acting analog of growth hormone-releasing hormone (GHRH), with <strong>Ipamorelin</strong>, a selective ghrelin receptor agonist (GHSR agonist). The synergistic effect of these two peptides is being studied for its role in stimulating endogenous growth hormone (GH) secretion with both immediate and prolonged activity. CJC-1295 (DAC) enables extended GH release due to its binding to serum albumin, while Ipamorelin contributes rapid GH pulse stimulation.</p>',58.00,NULL,NULL,5.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/CJC-1295DAC_Ipamorelin.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/cjc-1295dac-ipamorelin/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,11),(472,'PT-141','<p>PT-141 is a synthetic peptide analog of alpha-melanocyte-stimulating hormone (α-MSH). It has been extensively studied for its ability to activate melanocortin receptors, which are involved in a variety of physiological processes, including sexual function and energy regulation. PT-141 is provided in lyophilized powder form for research purposes focusing on sexual health and other physiological effects.</p>',24.00,NULL,NULL,10.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/PT-141.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/pt-141/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,54),(473,'GLOW Plus (BPC-157/GHK-Cu/TB-500/Thymosin Alpha-1 Blend)','<p>The &#8220;GLOW-Plus&#8221; Blend takes regenerative peptide research to the next level by incorporating Thymosin Alpha-1 into the proven combination of BPC-157, GHK-Cu, and TB-500. This powerful blend offers a comprehensive research platform for exploring advanced tissue regeneration, immune modulation, and skin health enhancement. Ideal for investigating the synergistic effects of peptides in cellular repair, inflammation reduction, and overall rejuvenation, this blend supports cutting-edge research in regenerative medicine and immunology.</p>',115.00,NULL,NULL,3.00,'in_stock','active',6,NULL,0,0,0,'https://purehealthpeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/GLOW-Plus.jpg','https://purehealthpeptides.com/product/glow-plus-bpc-157-ghk-cu-tb-500-thymosin-alpha-1-blend/','2025-12-04 15:07:17','2025-12-04 15:07:17',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,353),(474,'GLOW &#8211; BPC-157/GHK-Cu/TB-500 Blend','<p>The &#8220;GLOW&#8221; Blend combines the synergistic benefits of BPC-157, GHK-Cu, and TB-500 to provide a comprehensive research tool for regenerative studies. This innovative blend is designed to explore the combined effects of peptides that promote tissue repair, skin