nt laboratory testing</li>\n</ul>',95.00,NULL,NULL,1.00,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/GLP-2TZ-With-B12.png','https://simplepeptide.com/product/glp-2tz-capsules-with-b12/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 21:41:05',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,89),(669,'Orforglipron 6MG  90 Capsules','<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"243\"><strong>Orforglipron</strong> is a small-molecule compound used in research focused on metabolism, glucose control, and energy regulation. Its stable, non-peptide design allows scientists to study GLP-1 receptor activity without peptide instability concerns.</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-start=\"247\" data-end=\"315\">Studied for its impact on metabolic balance and glucose regulation</li>\n<li data-start=\"318\" data-end=\"389\">Non-peptide structure ensures stability and easy handling in research</li>\n<li data-start=\"392\" data-end=\"455\">Useful for exploring GLP-1 receptor pathways and energy control</li>\n</ul>',239.00,NULL,NULL,6.00,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Orforglipron-Peptide-Bottle.webp','https://simplepeptide.com/product/orforglipron/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,90),(670,'NeuroboliX Dissolving Strips','<p><strong>NeuroboliX </strong>Focus and Energy Dissolving Strips supports research studies on cognitive function, energy use, and metabolism.  The formula includes Tesofensine and 5-Amino-1MQ, providing a way for research studies to examine how this combination may effect stamina, focus, and mental clarity.  The fast-dissolving format also helps study sublingual delivery and absorption in a simple, effective way.</p>',139.99,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Simple-Strips-NeuroboliX-New.jpg','https://simplepeptide.com/product/neurobolix-dissolving-strips/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,408),(671,'IntimiX Dissolving Strips','<p><strong>IntimiX Dissolving Strips</strong> combines PT-141, Oxytocin, and Aminophenpyrolle for research studies pertaining to areas of vitality, behavioral response, and emotional pathways.  The fast-dissolving format allows researchers to study rapid absorption, sublingual delivery, and compound interaction in controlled environments.</p>',189.99,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Simple-Strips-Intimix-New.jpg','https://simplepeptide.com/product/intimix-dissolving-strips/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,409),(672,'EnergeniX Dissolvable Strips','<p><strong>EnergeniX Dissolvable Strips</strong> are designed for research exploring cellular energy, metabolic activity, and vitality pathways. Each strip contains NAD+, MOTS-C, and 5-Amino-1MQ—compounds studied for their roles in mitochondrial function and energy regulation. Their dissolvable format allows researchers to examine rapid absorption methods and delivery efficiency in controlled studies.</p>',160.99,NULL,NULL,NULL,'out_of_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Simple-Strips-EnergeniX-New.jpg','https://simplepeptide.com/product/energenix-disolvable-strips/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,410),(673,'SynaptiX Dissolvable Strips','<p><strong>SynaptiX</strong> Brain Boost Dissolvable Strips are designed for research studies in areas related to cognitive function, clarity, and sustained energy.  Each strip contains Paraxanthine, L-Theanine, Alpha-GPC, and B vitamins in a quick-dissolving format.  This allows for a convenient way to conduct clinical research on the effects of sublingual delivery and absorption efficiency in areas of focus, alertness, and energy balance.</p>',39.99,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Simple-Strips-SynaptiX-New.jpg','https://simplepeptide.com/product/synaptix-dissolvable-strips/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,411),(674,'Vitality Power Dissolving Strips','<div class=\"product-description\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\"><strong>Melts™ NAD+ Dissolving Strips</strong> are designed to support cellular energy, DNA repair, and metabolic health. Each fast-dissolving strip provides an easy, pill-free, and needle-free way to promote vitality, resilience, and healthy aging as part of your daily wellness routine.</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em 1.5em !important\">\n<li>Supports natural energy production and cellular renewal</li>\n<li>Encourages DNA repair and healthy metabolic function</li>\n<li>Offers a quick, convenient, and travel-friendly daily boost</li>\n</ul>\n</div>',59.99,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Melts™-NAD-Dissolving-Strips-Tin.png','https://simplepeptide.com/product/melts-nad-dissolving-strips/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,92),(675,'Sleep Dissolving Strips','<div class=\"product-description\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\"><strong>Melts™ Deep Sleep™ Dissolving Strips</strong> combine <strong>Melatonin</strong>, <strong>GABA</strong>, <strong>L-Theanine</strong>, and soothing botanicals in a fast-dissolving format. This balanced blend helps the body relax, supports healthy sleep patterns, and promotes restful, refreshing sleep.</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em 1.5em !important\">\n<li>Encourages deep relaxation and restful sleep</li>\n<li>Supports natural sleep cycles with gentle, non-habit-forming ingredients</li>\n<li>Dissolves quickly for easy, water-free use at home or on the go</li>\n</ul>\n</div>',39.99,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Melts™-Deep-Sleep™-Dissolving-Strips-Tin.png','https://simplepeptide.com/product/melts-deep-sleep-dissolving-strips/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,93),(676,'Brain Fuel Dissolving Strips','<div class=\"product-description\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\"><strong>Melts™ Brain Fuel™ Dissolving Strips</strong> combine <strong>Paraxanthine</strong>, <strong>L-Theanine</strong>, <strong>Alpha-GPC</strong>, and essential <strong>B vitamins</strong> to support focus, clarity, and balanced mental energy. This advanced blend helps promote calm alertness and sharper concentration without the crash that often comes from other sources.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em !important\">The fast-dissolving strips offer a convenient, pill-free way to stay sharp and energized. They work quickly on the tongue and are easy to use anytime—whether you’re at work, studying, or on the go. In addition, their portable and discreet design makes daily mental support simple, effective, and easy to maintain.</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0 0 1.5em 1.5em !important\">\n<li>Enhances focus, clarity, and sustained mental energy</li>\n<li>Delivers smooth, balanced alertness without a crash</li>\n<li>Dissolves quickly for on-the-go convenience and ease</li>\n</ul>\n</div>',36.99,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Melts-Recovery-Desolving-Strips.png','https://simplepeptide.com/product/melts-brain-fuel-dissolving-strips/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,94),(677,'Glow X Dissolvable Strips','<p data-start=\"107\" data-end=\"288\"><strong>Glow X Recovery Dissolvable Strips</strong> combine BPC-157, TB-500, and GHK-Cu in a quick-dissolving format for studies on cellular recovery, wellness pathways, and resilience mechanisms.</p>',199.99,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Simple-Strips-GlowX-New.jpg','https://simplepeptide.com/product/glow-x-dissolvable-strips/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,412),(678,'Tesamorelin/Ipamorelin 12/2MG','<p data-start=\"81\" data-end=\"299\">The TESA IPA peptide blend combines Tesamorelin and Ipamorelin, offering a dual approach to studying growth hormone release and its effects on metabolism, recovery, and cellular function in research applications.</p>\n<ul data-start=\"301\" data-end=\"511\">\n<li data-start=\"301\" data-end=\"361\">\n<p data-start=\"303\" data-end=\"361\">Tesamorelin mimics GHRH to stimulate pituitary signaling</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"362\" data-end=\"429\">\n<p data-start=\"364\" data-end=\"429\">Ipamorelin activates ghrelin receptors for selective GH release</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"430\" data-end=\"511\">\n<p data-start=\"432\" data-end=\"511\">Blend supports studies on muscle growth, fat metabolism, and sleep regulation</p>\n</li>\n</ul>',109.00,NULL,NULL,2.00,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/tesaipa.jpg','https://simplepeptide.com/product/tesamorelin-ipamorelin-blend/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,413),(679,'GLP-2TZ 100MG','<p data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"182\">GLP-2TZ 100MG is a research peptide that activates both GLP-1 and GIP receptors, giving scientists a reliable tool to study metabolism, energy balance, and glucose regulation.</p>\n<p data-start=\"184\" data-end=\"346\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">• Helps maintain glucose and metabolic stability<br data-start=\"232\" data-end=\"235\" />• Engages dual GLP-1 and GIP receptor pathways<br data-start=\"286\" data-end=\"289\" />• Suited for endocrinology and metabolic research studies</p>',425.00,NULL,NULL,100.00,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/GLP-2TZ-100MG.webp','https://simplepeptide.com/product/glp2-tz-100mg/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,97),(680,'SLU-PP-332 Capsules','<p data-start=\"120\" data-end=\"300\">SLU-PP-332 is a research-only ERR agonist designed to help scientists study energy balance, metabolism, and mitochondrial function.</p>\n<ul data-start=\"302\" data-end=\"489\">\n<li data-start=\"302\" data-end=\"361\">\n<p data-start=\"304\" data-end=\"361\">Supports research on ERR pathways and energy regulation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"362\" data-end=\"421\">\n<p data-start=\"364\" data-end=\"421\">Consistent and repeatable results</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"422\" data-end=\"489\">\n<p data-start=\"424\" data-end=\"489\">Investigated for roles in metabolism and hormone-linked biology</p>\n</li>\n</ul>',154.00,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/SLU.jpg','https://simplepeptide.com/product/slu-pp-332/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,71),(681,'Reta/Cag 12.5MG/2.5MG','<p data-start=\"104\" data-end=\"286\"><strong data-start=\"104\" data-end=\"129\">Reta/Cag 12.5MG/2.5MG</strong> is a research compound that combines <strong data-start=\"167\" data-end=\"182\">Retatrutide</strong> and <strong data-start=\"187\" data-end=\"203\">Cagrilintide</strong>, developed for scientific studies in weight management and metabolic regulation.</p>\n<p data-start=\"288\" data-end=\"319\"><strong data-start=\"288\" data-end=\"317\">Key Research Focus Areas:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"320\" data-end=\"547\">\n<li data-start=\"320\" data-end=\"401\">\n<p data-start=\"322\" data-end=\"401\">Dual-pathway approach to weight management through Retatrutide + Cagrilintide</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"402\" data-end=\"468\">\n<p data-start=\"404\" data-end=\"468\">Investigation of appetite control, satiety, and energy balance</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"469\" data-end=\"547\">\n<p data-start=\"471\" data-end=\"547\">Research into glucose regulation, insulin response, and overall metabolism</p>\n</li>\n</ul>',135.00,NULL,NULL,12.50,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025