rmulations on the market. This is not a defect but rather a result of its exceptional quality and concentration.</p>\n<p class=\"ai-optimize-35\"><strong>Please be aware that we do not offer refunds or exchanges on this product. By purchasing AOD, you acknowledge and accept these characteristics. </strong>To avoid this issue altogether we highly recommend researching Tesamorelin, which is far more effective for the use case based on published clinical data.</p>',45.00,NULL,NULL,5.00,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/AOD-9604.png','https://simplepeptide.com/product/aod-9604-5mg/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,47),(723,'Bacteriostatic Water 30ML','<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Please note: There is a current shortage of Hospira Brand bacteriostatic water which has caused prices to triple. As a result we have brought the 30ML Bacteriostatic Water in house for now although we will be adding Hospira Branded back in the next few weeks although the cost will be significantly higher.</p>\n<p>All Simple Peptide Bacteriostatic Water is made in a sterile lab using only food grade reagents to ensure purity and reliability.</p>\n<p>Our process includes:</p>\n<p><strong>Pharmaceutical-Grade Ingredients</strong><br />\nWe use only USP-certified benzyl alcohol and Sterile Water for Injection (SWFI). The final solution contains 0.9% benzyl alcohol to inhibit bacterial growth after opening, as per industry standard.</p>\n<p><strong>Sterile Environment Protocols</strong><br />\nAll compounding and vial filling takes place inside an ISO-classified laminar flow hood or biosafety cabinet. This minimizes particulate and microbial contamination and mirrors pharmaceutical cleanroom procedures.</p>\n<p><strong>Sterile Filtration</strong><br />\nThe solution is passed through a 0.22-micron pharmaceutical-grade sterile filter, ensuring the removal of any potential contaminants while preserving the integrity of the solution.</p>\n<p><strong>Medical-Grade Vial Packaging</strong><br />\nThe filtered solution is aseptically transferred into sterile, depyrogenated 10 mL glass vials, each sealed with tamper-evident caps and sterile rubber stoppers.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',18.00,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/BAC-H20-1.jpg','https://simplepeptide.com/product/bacteriostatic-water-30ml/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 19:00:08',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,342),(724,'Oxytocin 2MG','<p><span class=\"BxUVEf ILfuVd\" lang=\"en\"><span class=\"hgKElc\">Oxytocin is a peptide hormone and neuropeptide normally produced in the hypothalamus and released by the posterior pituitary.</span></span></p>',35.00,NULL,NULL,2.00,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/oxytocin.jpg','https://simplepeptide.com/product/oxytocin-2mg/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,33),(725,'Ipamorelin/CJC-1295 (w/o DAC)','<p><strong>Ipamorelin/CJC-1295 (no DAC)</strong> is a high-purity, synergistic blend designed for advanced research into growth hormone (GH) pathways.  This formulation combines a selective GH secretagogue (Ipamorelin) with a short-acting GHRH analogue (CJC-1295) to produce a strong, clean GH pulse.  It is the ideal compound for studying hormonal signaling and short-term metabolic responses with precision.</p>',65.00,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/IPACJC-1.jpg','https://simplepeptide.com/product/ipamorelin-cjc-1295-no-dac/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-05 14:10:43',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,11),(726,'LIPO PURE (MIC-B12)','<p class=\"ai-optimize-30\"><strong>NEW FORMULA FOR AUGUST 2025!!! OUR NEWEST FORMULA HAS BEEN UPGRADED TO 200MG OF L-CARNITINE PER ML.  THE BEST LIPO-MIC PRODUCT ON THE MARKET!</strong></p>\n<p class=\"ai-optimize-30\">LIPO Pure is a meticulously formulated injectable