5000iu/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,134),(748,'Glutathione 1500MG','<p><strong>Glutathione</strong> is a tripeptide antioxidant made of glutamine, glycine, and cysteine. Researchers study it for its ability to reduce oxidative stress, recycle other antioxidants, and support redox balance, making it a valuable tool for exploring cellular defense and resilience in laboratory settings.</p>',75.00,NULL,NULL,1500.00,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/GLUTATHIONE-1.jpg','https://simplepeptide.com/product/glutathione/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,8),(749,'Epitalon 10MG','<p class=\"ai-optimize-25\">Epithalon (Epitalon) is a synthetic derivative of epithalamin and a potential modulator of telomerase, the enzyme that maintains and protects the telomere caps at the ends of chromosomes (strands of DNA).</p>',33.00,NULL,NULL,10.00,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/epitalon.webp','https://simplepeptide.com/product/epitalon-10mg/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,49),(750,'Thymosin Alpha 1','<p><strong>Thymosin Alpha-1</strong> is a research peptide that supports studies on immune system activity and T cell proliferation. It provides scientists with a reliable tool for exploring immune regulation, balance, and cellular defense in controlled laboratory settings.</p>',86.00,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/THYMOSIN.jpg','https://simplepeptide.com/product/thymosin-alpha-1/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-04 17:28:45',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,48),(751,'BPC-157 500MCG','<p><strong>BPC-157 500MCG</strong> is a fragment of Body Protection Compound 157 that comes from naturally occurring gastric juices. Researchers use it in controlled laboratory settings to study cell activity, structural behavior, and basic molecular stab