e in cellular function, structural balance, and broader biological processes.</p>\n<h3></h3>',65.00,NULL,NULL,NULL,'in_stock','active',9,NULL,0,0,0,'https://simplepeptide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/tb-500.webp','https://simplepeptide.com/product/tb-500/','2025-12-04 17:28:45','2025-12-05 19:39:18',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,120),(754,'FOX04-DRI (10mg)','',200.00,NULL,NULL,10.00,'in_stock','active',10,NULL,0,0,0,'https://libertypeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/peptides-FOX04-DRI-10mg-1-scaled.webp','https://libertypeptides.com/product/fox04-dri-10mg/','2025-12-05 21:16:11','2025-12-05 21:16:11',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,428),(755,'Pinealon (20mg)','',55.00,NULL,NULL,20.00,'in_stock','active',10,NULL,0,0,0,'https://libertypeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/peptides-Pinealon-20mg-scaled.webp','https://libertypeptides.com/product/pinealon-20mg/','2025-12-05 21:16:11','2025-12-05 21:16:11',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,29),(756,'GHK-Cu, KPV, BPC-157, TB-500 80mg (KLOW Blend)','',140.00,NULL,NULL,80.00,'in_stock','active',10,NULL,0,0,0,'https://libertypeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Blends-GHK-CuBPC-157TB-500KPV-50-10-10-10mg-scaled.png','https://libertypeptides.com/product/ghk-cu-kpv-bpc-157-tb-500-50-10-10-10/','2025-12-05 21:16:11','2025-12-05 21:16:11',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,3),(757,'ARA-290, BPC-157, TB-500 (16/2/2mg Blend)','',74.00,NULL,NULL,2.00,'in_stock','active',10,NULL,0,0,0,'https://libertypeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Blends-ARA-290BPC-157TB-500-16-2-2mg-scaled.webp','https://libertypeptides.com/product/ara-290-bpc-157-tb-500-16-2-2mg-blend/','2025-12-05 21:16:11','2025-12-05 21:16:11',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,20),(758,'Survodutide (5mg)','',82.00,66.00,NULL,5.00,'in_stock','active',10,NULL,0,0,0,'https://libertypeptides.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/peptides-Survodutide-5mg-scaled.png','https://libertypeptides.com/product/survodutide-5mg/','2025-12-05 21:16:11','2025-12-05 21:16:11',0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,391),(759,'Hexarelin, CJC 1295 no DAC (5/5mg Blend)','',9